(12, 'Sky City Hotel Dhaka', 'Well-appointed rooms, multiple dining spots, an exclusive spa and a host of upscale amenities await you for a delightful stay at this luxurious property.\r\nThis splendid property is situated on Shiddeshwari Circular Road in Dhaka, Bangladesh. Set a few minutes away from the Bangladesh National Museum, this property is just a short drive away from the 17th-century Lalbagh Fort.\r\nThe property features multiple dining options to thrill your taste buds. There is a luxurious spa where you can soothe your mind and body.The property features a well-equipped gym for your fitness routine. There are state-of-the-art event venues where you can host impressive events. The property provides access to high-speed Wi-Fi for your convenience.The property facilitates on-site parking so that you can have a hassle-free driving experience.', NULL, 4, '01313368377', NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', '47 Shiddeshwari Circular Road, Dhaka 1217', 'Hindi, English, Urdu and Arabic', NULL, 'hotels/main/gTn04ZWJ232FIa3NEIYN3hvguRYouainvYawgCLk.jpg', '2025-07-20 09:32:54', '2025-07-20 09:32:54', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Kamlapur Railway Station  Railway  1.8 Km|  Directorate of Food & Drugs Administration  Tourist Attraction  1.9 Km| Baitul Mukarram Mosque  Religious Place  2.4 Km | Baitul Mukarram Mosque  Religious Place  2.4 Km| Dhakeshwari Temple  Temple  5 Km|', 1, NULL, 1),
