(20, 'Hotel D-Palace', 'Hotel D-Palace in Dhaka offers air-conditioned rooms with private bathrooms, bathrobes, and free toiletries. Each room includes a work desk, TV, and wardrobe, ensuring a pleasant stay.\r\n Guests can enjoy an à la carte breakfast with vegetarian and halal options. The hotel provides free on-site private parking and a welcoming reception staffed with English-speaking personnel.\r\n Located in Ashkona, the hotel is a 5-minute walk from Dhaka Airport Railway Station. Nearby attractions include Uttara University (2.5 mi), Armed Forces Medical College (3.7 mi), and North South University (3.7 mi).', NULL, 3, '01894-782070', NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', '403, Haji Komoruddin Tower, Ashkona, Hajj Camp, Dakshinkhan, Dhaka-1230, Bangladesh.', 'English, Bangla', NULL, 'hotels/main/8IVtPuExa9LsCLPt9I0vXlFEwzSEahiasc74eT6y.jpg', '2025-07-21 04:29:58', '2025-07-21 04:29:58', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', 41, NULL, 'Located in Ashkona, the hotel is a 5-minute walk from Dhaka Airport Railway Station|. Nearby attractions include Uttara University (2.5 mi)|, Armed Forces Medical College (3.7 mi)|, and North South University (3.7 mi).|', 2, NULL, 1),
(21, 'Babylon Hotel & Serviced Apartment', 'Babylon Hotel & Serviced Apartment in Dhaka offers family rooms with air-conditioning, private bathrooms, and city views. Each room includes a tea and coffee maker, work desk, and free WiFi\r\nGuests can enjoy a garden, terrace, and rooftop pool. The aparthotel provides free bicycles, a fitness room, and a steam room. Additional amenities include a lounge, children\'s playground, and outdoor seating areas.\r\nThe on-site restaurant serves Chinese, Indian, local, Asian, international, and European cuisines. Breakfast options include continental, American, full English, vegetarian, and halal.\r\n Located 5 km from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport, the aparthotel is near Armed Forces Medical College (2 km) and North South University (5 km).', NULL, 3, '01974-225555', NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'Eastern Road, Baridhara DOHS, 1206 Dhaka, Bangladesh', 'Hindi, English, Urdu', NULL, 'hotels/main/MNlMKFONdVWVtyceONRBKn6JvD09gHfcPe7tpQHM.jpg', '2025-07-21 05:28:02', '2025-07-21 05:28:02', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Located 5 km  from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport, | the aparthotel is near Armed Forces Medical College (2 km) | North South University (5 km). |', NULL, NULL, 1),
(22, 'Hotel Luxury Inn', 'Conveniently located in the Uttara district of Dhaka, Hotel Luxury Inn is set 1.8 km from Uttara University, 3 km from IUBAT and 4.6 km from Dhaka Airport Railway Station. Featuring a terrace, the 3-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The accommodation offers room service, a 24-hour front desk and organising tours for guests. At the hotel, each room is fitted with a wardrobe. All rooms have a desk and a flat-screen TV, and some units at Hotel Luxury Inn have a balcony. A Full English/Irish, Asian or vegetarian breakfast can be enjoyed at the property. The restaurant at the accommodation specialises in Indian, Thai and Asian cuisine. Armed Forces Medical College is 10 km from Hotel Luxury Inn, while Independent University Bangladesh is 10 km away. Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport is 7 km from the property, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.', NULL, 3, '01711-757454', NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', '06 Lake Drive Road, Sector# 07, Uttara,, Uttara, Dhaka', 'Hindi, English, Urdu', NULL, 'hotels/main/qbahbenpy3r2ZJrO7ZDbC8mw3eJMhlIVR1rqYnJP.jpg', '2025-07-21 07:17:38', '2025-07-21 07:17:38', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Uttara 11 No Central Park 950 m | 11 No Sector Park 1 km | Uttara 12 No. Sector Park 1.2 km |Uttra Kalyan Samiti Sector 4 1.3 km | Gate Two Walk Way 1.4 km |', NULL, NULL, 1),
