(47, 'Hotel Water Orchid', 'Hotel Water Orchid is an excellent choice for travelers visiting Cox\'s Bazar, offering many helpful amenities designed to enhance your stay.\r\n\r\nAs your “home away from home,” the hotel rooms offer air conditioning, a seating area, and a sofa.\r\n\r\nGuests have access to a 24 hour front desk, room service, and a concierge while staying at Hotel Water Orchid. And, as an added convenience, there is free parking available to guests.\r\n\r\nTravelers looking to enjoy some shrimp can head to Poushee Restaurant. Otherwise, you may want to check out an Asian restaurant such as Mermaid Cafe, EFC - A Live Fish Restaurant, or Poushee Restaurant.\r\n\r\nEnjoy your stay in Cox\'s Bazar!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Cox\'sbazar', 'Block C, Plot 25, Kolatoli, Cox\'s Bazar 4700 Bangladesh', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/NwnqlSG6N8hpd6nAfRIQ4TdUwHNSI0ZvfvviCeaH.jpg', '2025-07-22 07:55:23', '2025-07-22 07:55:23', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Police Lines Ground 1.6 km | Coxs Bazar Ban Samprasaran and Prosikshon Kendra 3.9 km | College Ground 4.5 km | Nilima 13 km | Cox Bazar Botanical Garden 17 km', NULL, NULL, 1),
