(55, 'Lakeshore Banani', 'Offering an a fitness center, Lakeshore Banani is located in Dhaka.  The Banani Railway Station and the Banani Bus Station are 0.6 mi. Free WiFi access is available.\r\n\r\nEach air-conditioned room here will provide you with a cable TV, a seating area and a mini-bar. Complete with a microwave, the dining area also has an electric kettle. Featuring a shower, private bathroom also comes with a bathtub and bathrobes.\r\n\r\nFacilities offered at Lakeshore Banani include a shared lounge, a tour desk and luggage storage. The property offers free parking.\r\n\r\nThe Gulshan Lake is 0.6 mi, the Baridhara Lake is 1.9 mi and the Jamuna Future Park Mall is 3.1 mi. The Shah Jalal International Airport is 5 mi away.\r\n\r\nDining highlights include a multi-cuisine restaurant. 24-hour room service is available.', NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'House 81, Road 13/A, Block D, Banani, Banani, Dhaka, Bangladesh, 1213', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/973jvskugxNTg8GuHCeSooeZDoRvRjVUpvdUYLLh.jpg', '2025-07-22 10:38:38', '2025-07-22 10:38:38', 6, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(56, 'Richmond Hotel & Suites', 'Located just 0.8 mi from Shahjalal International Airport, Richmond Hotel & Suites operates a 24-hour front desk to ease check-in and check-out at all hours. Free Wi-Fi is available in all areas.\r\n\r\nGeorge’s Kitchen, the in-house restaurant serves regional, Indian, Thai and Chinese cuisine. Room service can be used for in-room dining comforts during the hours available.\r\n\r\nRichmond Hotel & Suites is 0.9 mi from Airport Railway Station and 1 mi from the Airport Bus Station, Dhaka. The Jatiyo Sriti Shoudho, the national martyr’s monument, is 6.2 mi, Jatiyo Sangsad Bhaban, the national parliament, is 9.3 mi from it while The Bangladesh National Museum is 11 mi away.\r\n\r\nThe air-conditioned rooms feature modern décor, a flat-screen satellite TV and seating area. Mini-bar, ironing facilities and work desk are included in the rooms too. The private bathrooms are equipped with a bathtub, hairdryer and free toiletries.\r\n\r\nLaundry with dry cleaning, currency exchange and luggage storage facilities are available. Ticketing services can be requested.', NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'House-02, Road-10, Sector-01, Uttara, Uttara, 1230 Dhaka, Bangladesh', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/bfAT8NfrTA2Wc7vqpw2qkbXVoKF93oK0tz15TIxz.jpg', '2025-07-22 11:04:22', '2025-07-22 11:04:22', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Uttra Kalyan Samiti Sector 4 1.4 km| Apbn Maath 1.7 km| Uttara 11 No Central Park 2.6 km| 11 No Sector Park 2.7 km| Uttara 12 No. Sector Park 3 km| Riya Garden 3.4 km| Gate Two Walk Way 3.5 km| Can-do Play Park 4.5 km| Jamuna Future Park 7 km| Baridhara Dohs Park 7 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
