(62, 'Rezala Restaurant Catering & Residence', 'A stay at Rezala Restaurant Catering & Residence places you in the heart of Dhaka, within a 10-minute drive of International Convention City Bashundhara and Jamuna Future Park. This luxury guesthouse is 5.2 mi (8.4 km) from Bangladesh Army Stadium and 6.3 mi (10.1 km) from Sher-e-Bangla Cricket Stadium.\r\nMake use of convenient amenities such as concierge services, a hair salon, and wedding services. Additional amenities at this guesthouse include a communal living room, a picnic area, and charcoal grills.\r\nGrab a bite to eat at one of the guesthouse\'s 20 restaurants, or stay in and take advantage of the 24-hour room service. Snacks are also available at the 20 coffee shops/cafes. A complimentary cooked-to-order breakfast is served daily from 9:30 AM to 10:30 AM.\r\nFeatured amenities include complimentary wired internet access, a 24-hour business center, and dry cleaning/laundry services. Event facilities at this guesthouse consist of a conference center and meeting rooms.\r\nMake yourself at home in one of the 6 air-conditioned rooms featuring Smart televisions. Your Select Comfort bed comes with down comforters and premium bedding. Complimentary wireless internet access keeps you connected, and satellite programming is available for your entertainment. Private bathrooms with showers feature rainfall showerheads and designer toiletries.', NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'House # 03 Road -13, Uttara, Tejgaon Circle, Dhaka Division, 1230, Bangladesh', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/DILz7Hrw5lFageY3DwRtjwsca3rDqNfL2u6wb9bZ.webp', '2025-07-23 04:35:43', '2025-07-23 04:35:43', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', 6, NULL, 'Dhaka Imperial Hospital 20.9 km| Shakil Pharmacy 21.5 km| Turag General Hospital 22.5 km| Shaheed Ahsanullah General Hospital 22.6 km| Shahid Ahsan Ullah Master Stadium 23.1 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
(63, 'World Beach Resort Cox\'s Bazar', 'Featuring Wi-Fi throughout the property, World Beach Resort Kelatali is a mere 1.4 km from Cox\'s Bazar Sea Beach. This Kelatali hotel also includes a car park.\r\n\r\nThe centre of Kelatali can be reached within a 5-minute walk. Radiant Fish World Aquarium is within a 10-minute drive of the hotel, while Cox\'s Bazar airport is 10 km from it. Kolatoli Sea Beach is located only a stone\'s throw from the accommodation.\r\n\r\nBathrooms include a separate toilet and a shower, along with such comforts as bath sheets and slippers.\r\n\r\nGuests can have breakfast in the restaurant.', NULL, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Cox\'s Bazar, Bangladesh', 'Kolatoli Road, Cox\'s Bazar, Bangladesh', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/N038NxJibd3gxmpgR85VoT60Qs8QjVrTdS1nixaP.jpg', '2025-07-23 04:50:39', '2025-07-23 04:50:39', 1, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, '0.35 km from Kolatoli Beach | 1.3 km from Sugondha Sea Beach | 5.2 km from Cox\'s Bazar Airport | 0.15 km from Kolatoli Bus Stand', NULL, NULL, 1),
