(71, 'Empyrean Dhaka City Centre', 'Empyrean Dhaka City Centre in Dhaka offers family rooms with air-conditioning, private bathrooms, and city views. Each room includes a work desk, minibar, and free WiFi.\r\n The family-friendly restaurant serves Chinese, Indian, American, Thai, Brazilian, international, and barbecue grill cuisines. Guests can enjoy brunch, lunch, dinner, and high tea in a traditional, modern, or romantic ambience.\r\nThe hotel features a fitness centre, terrace, and garden. Additional amenities include a lounge, outdoor fireplace, beauty services, and free on-site parking.\r\n Located 7 km from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport, the hotel is near attractions such as Bangladesh University of Textiles (2 km) and BRAC University (3 km). Boating is available in the surroundings.', NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', NULL, 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/D8CWi5uOKbW4QbFDJGnJs5c1hf1TDVcKD4CvRdWx.jpg', '2025-07-23 07:26:08', '2025-07-23 07:26:08', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Field 450 m Boishakhi Park 2.9 km| Banani Blues Fc Field 3.2 km| DR Fozle Rabbi Park 3.4 km| Shahid Dr Fazle Rabbi Park 3.5 km| School Ground 3.7 km| Gulshan Youth Club 4.7 km| Gulshan Lake Park 4.7 km| Apartment Recreational Ground 5 km| President Justice Shahabuddin Ahmed Park 5 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
(72, 'Green Peak Resorts', 'Experience Largest Infinity Pool\r\nTake a dip in our iconic infinity pool, perfectly placed to offer stunning views of the surrounding hills. The perfect spot to relax, unwind, and soak in the tranquility of nature.\r\n\r\nSituated near Bandarban City\r\nEco friendly tree house\r\nInfinity pool with a view\r\nComplimentary buffet breakfast\r\nFamily friendly environment\r\nContinental restaurant & tribal food', NULL, 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '55CM+324, Meghla (Opposite to TTC), Chittagong - Bandarban Hwy', NULL, 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/UkcEHYBzCdDvll8XFSbpLOqfsT3XI43KjS0wizdn.jpg', '2025-07-23 07:31:12', '2025-07-23 07:31:12', 10, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, '0.6 km from Meghla Tourism Complex | 3.2 km from নিলাচল লাভ পয়েন্ট, Nilachal Rd | 3.8 km from Thanchi Bus Stop, Bandarban | 4.7 km from Lama Bus Station, Z1811, Bandarban', NULL, NULL, 1),
(73, 'Hotel Tower Inn', 'Hotel Tower Inn in Chittagong offers a comfortable and convenient stay close to the city center. This 3-star hotel features well-appointed rooms and amenities such as a fitness center, restaurant, and complimentary parking. Guests can enjoy city views and take advantage of the airport shuttle service for added convenience. With thoughtful services and an ideal location, it\'s a popular choice for both business and leisure travelers.', NULL, 3, '01967776777', 'bookmebdltd@gmail.com', NULL, 1, 'Chattogram', '183 jubilee road, Chittagong, Bangladesh', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/Cttms8WNhLh1415ByCrxtCXCuDVnbXACN8CBOiXi.jpg', '2025-07-23 07:59:27', '2025-07-23 07:59:27', 5, 'single , double', NULL, NULL, 'Near Chittagong Railway station | 0.4 km from Kotwali Thana', NULL, NULL, 1),
(74, 'Hotel Hillton Bandarban', 'Hotel Hotel Hillton is situated at Bus Stand, Bandarban Main Road, Chittagong, Bangladesh. There are VIP Suite, Royal Suite, Super Deluxe, Deluxe, Couple + Couple, Couple + Single and Couple/Single room facilities in this hotel. There are AC and Non AC rooms are available in this Hotel. They have a well-decorated conference room with the capacity of over 100 people. Hotel Hillton has their own Restaurant. They provide delicious dishes with Chinese, Thai and Bengali food items at reasonable price. They offer special discount in off season for non AC rooms and group booking for long stay. Checkin time is 12:01pm and checkout time from Hotel Hillton is at 11:30am.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Bus Stand, Bandarban Main Road, Chittagong, Bangladesh.', NULL, 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/NbeS5eTvZygRXw6oYYE7Wev3uxffIuXWzYg1NOhT.jpg', '2025-07-23 08:52:50', '2025-07-23 08:52:50', 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.6 km from Meghla Tourism Complex | 3.2 km from নিলাচল লাভ পয়েন্ট, Nilachal Rd | 3.8 km from Thanchi Bus Stop, Bandarban | 4.7 km from Lama Bus Station, Z1811, Bandarban', NULL, NULL, 1),
(75, 'Sea Shell Residence - Dhaka', 'Sea Shell Residence in Dhaka offers recently renovated aparthotel rooms with private bathrooms, air-conditioning, and modern amenities. Family rooms are available, and the property is pet-friendly.\r\nThe family-friendly restaurant serves brunch, lunch, dinner, and high tea with halal, vegetarian, and dairy-free options. Cuisines include Chinese, British, Indian, American, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Malaysian, Mexican, pizza, seafood, Thai, Asian, and international.\r\n Located 5 km from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport and less than 1 km from Uttara University, the aparthotel provides free WiFi and a 24-hour front desk. Nearby attractions include Dhaka Airport Railway Station (2.9 km) and IUBAT (4 km).', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'Dhaka - Mymensingh Highway, Uttara, Dhaka', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/oCVj6I8Zl9baNm7Gfv9EAS1R4r5xyxsh9Dqw5KNx.jpg', '2025-07-23 09:13:10', '2025-07-23 09:13:10', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Uttra Kalyan Samiti Sector 4 700 m| Apbn Maath 950 m| Uttara 11 No Central Park 2.2 km| 11 No Sector Park 2.3 km| Uttara 12 No. Sector Park 2.7 km| Gate Two Walk Way 3.1 km| Riya Garden 3.3 km| Can-do Play Park 3.7 km| Jamuna Future Park 7 km| Baridhara Dohs Park 7 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
(76, 'The Elite Residence Dhaka Airport', 'The Elite Residence Dhaka Airport in Dhaka offers 4-star comfort with spacious rooms featuring air-conditioning, private bathrooms, and modern amenities. Guests enjoy free WiFi, flat-screen TVs, and comfortable seating areas.\r\nThe hotel offers spa facilities, a fitness centre, a serene garden, and a terrace. Additional services include massage treatments, beauty services, and wellness packages. A family-friendly restaurant serves a variety of cuisines, including Chinese, Indian, and Italian.\r\nSituated 3 km from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport, the hotel is close to Uttara University (14-minute walk) and Dhaka Airport Railway Station (2 km). Nearby attractions include IUBAT and North South University, each 7 km away.', NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'Road # 11, Sector #4, Uttara, Bangladesh House# 50,, Uttara, Dhaka', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/lx1YsgG2D0n9LX7JBf4e6T2ilZpIE92WBy6dS6ji.jpg', '2025-07-23 09:35:09', '2025-07-23 09:35:09', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(77, 'FARS Hotel & Resorts - BAR-Buffet-Pool-SPA', 'Located just 1 km from National Museum, FARS Hotel & Resorts - BAR-Buffet-Pool-SPA feature a rooftop swimming, fitness centre and spa and wellness centre. To entertain the guests they have a games room. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.\r\n\r\nFARS Hotel & Resorts - BAR-Buffet-Pool-SPA is located 500 metres from Bangladesh Secretariat, 1.5 km from Kamalapur Railway Station and 2 km from Lalbagh Fort. The Shahjalal International Airport is 10 km away.\r\n\r\nEach air-conditioned room comes with a minibar, electric kettle and flat-screen satellite TV. The private bathroom includes a bathtub, free toiletries and shower.\r\n\r\nTo assist the guests, FARS Hotel & Resorts - BAR-Buffet-Pool-SPA operates a 24-hour front desk. They provide services like packed lunches, luggage storage and laundry. Guests can pamper themselves at the massage parlour. A tour desk is available to make travel arrangements. A car can be rented for sightseeing.\r\n\r\nGuests can sample a variety of Indian, Bangladeshi, Thai, Chinese and Continental cuisines at Our Feast, the in-house restaurant. Room service is available.', NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', '212, Shahid Syed Nazrul Islam Sharani (Bijoynagar) Dhaka-1000, Bangladesh, Dhaka', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/IUuU5sARDTvR5qkoY7weRIXKu5rSSozxJNftaQZp.jpg', '2025-07-23 09:53:35', '2025-07-23 09:53:35', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Ramna Park 850 m| Rajarbag police line physical training ground 1.7 km| BUET Tennis Court 2.6 km| Muslimbag Tower Math 3.9 km| Iraqi Math 3.9 km| Apartment Recreational Ground 6 km| DR Fozle Rabbi Park 6 km| Field 6 km| Shahid Dr Fazle Rabbi Park 6 km| School Ground 6 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
(78, 'Hotel Hill View', 'Comfortable Accommodations: Hotel Hill View in Bandarban offers family rooms with air-conditioning, balconies, and private bathrooms. Each room features mountain or city views, a sofa bed, work desk, and free toiletries.\r\n\r\nDining and Leisure: Guests can enjoy a restaurant serving American and Asian breakfast with local specialities. The hotel also provides a coffee shop, karaoke, and evening entertainment. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.\r\n\r\nConvenient Facilities: The hotel offers a garden, minimarket, and paid shuttle service. Additional amenities include a 24-hour front desk, room service, and free on-site private parking.\r\n\r\nAccessible Location: Shah Amanat International Airport is 83 km away. The property is situated on Bus Station Road, providing easy access to local attractions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Bus Station Road, 4600 Bāndarban, Bangladesh', NULL, 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/Gb3emXGnEj6OsQJxQaPHS2j5DLEs57k2ZAHJFXOJ.jpg', '2025-07-23 10:16:48', '2025-07-23 10:16:48', 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(80, 'Hotel New Kalabgan Residential', 'Hotel New Kalabgan Residential in Dhaka offers family rooms with private bathrooms, air-conditioning, and free WiFi. Each room includes a work desk, TV, and free toiletries.\r\nGuests benefit from a 24-hour front desk, room service, and a range of amenities. Additional services include a work desk, TV, and slippers.\r\nLocated 6.2 mi from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport, the hotel is near attractions such as World University of Bangladesh (less than 0.6 mi), Dhaka Tribune (9-minute walk), and Bangladesh Medical College (1.2 mi). Boating is available in the surrounding area.', NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'Brothers Mansion 1st Floor, Dhaka', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/WE7UjvfS4twSe8MRxTYYlsYERXOIri3XAOqa8rIp.jpg', '2025-07-23 10:33:42', '2025-07-23 10:33:42', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'School Ground 2.3 km| Iraqi Math 2.4 km| BUET Tennis Court 2.7 km| Ramna Park 3.6 km| Field 3.7 km| Rajarbag police line physical training ground 5 km| College Play Ground 5 km| Muslimbag Tower Math 5 km| DR Fozle Rabbi Park 5 km| Shahid Dr Fazle Rabbi Park 6 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
(81, 'Hotel Shaikat', 'Hotel Shaikat is very popular place for people coming by Train. It is very near to Chittagong Railway Station. It offers good quality room service with amenities.', NULL, NULL, '01967776777', 'bookmebdltd@gmail.com', NULL, 1, 'Chattogram', 'Station Road, Chattogram', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/MrA3XUjxRC92k3WMLzroGnldwoKqXXo1dttwfWH5.jpg', '2025-07-23 10:44:39', '2025-07-23 10:44:39', 5, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Near Chittagong Railway station | 1 km from Kotwali Thana | Near BRTC Chattogram', NULL, NULL, 1),
(82, 'Hotel Prime Inn Mirpur', 'Hotel Prime Inn Mirpur in Dhaka offers family rooms with private bathrooms, air-conditioning, and free WiFi. Each room includes a TV, sofa, and tiled floors.\r\nGuests benefit from a 24-hour front desk, concierge service, minimarket, housekeeping, room service, and elevator access. Additional amenities include free toiletries, shower, slippers, and air-conditioning.\r\n: Located 5 mi from Hazrat Shahjalal International Airport, the hotel is a 19-minute walk from BUBT. Nearby attractions include Southeast University and AIUB, each 3.7 mi away.', NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'Mirpur Rd House-6, Block-A, lift-7, Mirpur, Dhaka', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/Hqp4r7kk18poHAnN0duyV6SmlGaEwxfID5YBwgW9.jpg', '2025-07-23 11:08:16', '2025-07-23 11:08:16', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Babu Land Indoor Playground 150 m| Dhaka Jila Parishad Sheikh Rasel Shishu Park 1.7 km| Harun Mollho Eidgah Park O Khalar Math 2.2 km| College Play Ground 2.5 km| Banani Blues Fc Field 4.3 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
