(85, 'Hotel Marina International Ltd', 'With a stay at Hotel Marina International Ltd, you\'ll be centrally located in Dhaka, just a 4-minute walk from St. Mary\'s Cathedral and 7 minutes by foot from Ramna Park. This hotel is 0.6 mi (1 km) from Baily Road and 1 mi (1.6 km) from Old High Court Building.\r\nAt Hotel Marina International Ltd, enjoy a satisfying meal at the restaurant.\r\nFree self parking is available onsite.\r\nMake yourself at home in one of the 49 guestrooms. Complimentary wireless internet access is available to keep you connected. Bathrooms with bathtubs or showers are provided. Conveniences include desks, and housekeeping is provided daily.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', '5th to 8th floor, Bhuiyan Mansion, 74 Kakrail Cir, Dhaka 1000', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/CS92MH37v6ygjxPNjuHYlbahlc1x4H1KjJjeQC4p.webp', '2025-07-24 04:19:05', '2025-07-24 04:19:05', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', 49, NULL, 'Dhaka, just a 4-minute walk from St. Mary\'s Cathedral and 7 minutes by foot from Ramna Park|  This hotel is 0.6 mi (1 km) from Baily Road|   1 mi (1.6 km) from Old High Court Building.|', 4, NULL, 1),
(86, 'Anchorage The Residence', 'Anchorage The Residence has a fitness centre, garden, a shared lounge and terrace in Dhaka. Featuring a restaurant, the 4-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The accommodation features a shared kitchen, free shuttle service and currency exchange for guests. All rooms at the hotel are fitted with a seating area and a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. Some rooms have a kitchen with a fridge, an oven and a microwave. At Anchorage, The Residence rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels. The area is popular for cycling, and car hire is available at the accommodation. Speaking English and Hindi, staff are always on hand to help at the reception.', NULL, 4, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Dhaka', 'House 14, Road 18, Sector 4, Uttara, Uttara, Dhaka', 'Bangla, English', NULL, 'hotels/main/Md7cHSlnuWuYdu1dokQQcF4dlMjWUfCXBxMI6srg.jpg', '2025-07-24 04:41:46', '2025-07-24 04:41:46', 6, 'Single,Couple,triple, Familly', NULL, NULL, 'Uttra Kalyan Samiti Sector 4 450 m| Apbn Maath 1 km| Uttara 11 No Central Park 1.8 km| 11 No Sector Park 1.8 km| Uttara 12 No. Sector Park 2.3 km|', NULL, NULL, 1),
