(1, 172, 1, 'Locations that will be covered in this tour:', '<p>Enjoy a traditional Tanguar Haor experience in the most classical way. Stay in a wooden boat for two days and get immersed in the majestic beauty of this popular Wetland of Sunamganj. Explore the scenic beauty of the land and get enchanted by the magical attractions nearby. This tour is ideal for travelers who want to explore Tanguar haor.</p><p><strong>Locations that will be covered in this tour:</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Package Price for Jolnibash:</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 6,500 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Attached Bath for 2 People BDT 7,500 Per Person</p><p>Family Connecting Cabin-&nbsp;Attached Bath for 5 people BDT 7,000 Per Person</p><p>Bunker Bed - Common Bath for 5 People BDT 6,000 Per Person</p>', 'facility_images/99Sxmk3b96dPM3ccvs2TLCfIJYrDkgDkaORuUB1A.jpg', 1, 1, '2024-12-01 16:59:00', '2024-12-03 07:16:57', '7'),
(2, 172, 1, 'Locations that will be covered in this tour:', '<ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>&nbsp;</li></ul>', 'facility_images/ih12gfiaFzxfSvVK6E2MhiTL1VKp7fMwqbOd8OX4.jpg', 1, 2, '2024-12-01 16:59:53', '2024-12-01 17:48:48', '7'),
(3, 172, 2, NULL, '<p>2 Days and 1 Night</p><p>&nbsp;<strong>Duration</strong> : 2 days</p>', 'facility_images/mhcdihDSx2uPxcHe8wCzM87lnWwQRtzf1mEgYuI2.jpg', 1, 2, '2024-12-01 17:00:59', '2024-12-01 17:00:59', '8'),
(4, 172, 3, 'Pick-up:', '<p>Saheb Bari Jetty, Sunamganj</p>', 'facility_images/uFGTk3C8QDGjcN9xmTL7h6GQ8dwALLw7QsMl1UnK.jpg', 1, 4, '2024-12-01 17:03:15', '2024-12-01 17:03:15', '9'),
(5, 172, 5, NULL, '<p>Located in north-eastern Bangladesh, Tanguar haor is a river basin and a unique wetland ecosystem of national importance. The tour is ideal for you if you want to experience both adventures and serenity. You’ll have a traditional wooden boat with the necessary amenities as your home during the tour. During the tour, you’ll have mouth-watering delicacies more than three times a day while watching the beauty of the wetland from your private boat. The tour will also let you explore the picturesque beauty of Shimul Bagan, bathe in the mirror-like clear water, visit the popular lakes, and enjoy the view of the hills around. Hence, the tour will give you both tranquility to your soul and stories to tell.</p>', 'facility_images/BUxhCCnEsi1HGoQ1KmUMK9r2cFCsmn5x5oJTJFXJ.jpg', 1, 4, '2024-12-01 17:19:06', '2024-12-01 17:19:06', '11'),
(6, 172, 5, 'Places that will be covered in this tour are', '<ul><li>Tekerghat</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake/ Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Tanguar Haor Watch Tower</li><li>Koroch tree forest</li></ul>', 'facility_images/yzPIM9zJ0uHAN4CNFoHYGv0BQ3pkhBIaOCK3OvA2.jpg', 1, 6, '2024-12-01 17:20:13', '2024-12-01 17:20:13', '11'),
(7, 172, 5, 'Food Menu', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>1st day-</p><ul><li>Breakfast: Chicken khichuri, egg curry, begun bhaja, salad and water</li><li>Morning Snacks: Dry cake/biscuits/fruits and tea.</li><li>Lunch: Plain rice, chicken Curry/fish Curry, daal, vegetables, fish bhorta, and water.</li><li>Evening snacks: Noodles and tea</li><li>Dinner: Plain rice, duck curry, bhorta, daal, vegetables, salad and water.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>2nd Day-</p><ul><li>Breakfast: Chicken khichuri, egg curry, begun bhaja, salad and water</li><li>Morning Snacks: Dry cake/biscuits/fruits and tea.</li><li>Lunch: Plain rice, chicken Curry/fish Curry, daal, vegetables, fish bhorta, and water.</li><li>Evening snacks: Noodles and tea.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/7fA7gBPwLmky5p91zpWyUwf2fj2kzIozqeqzd2wZ.jpg', 1, 8, '2024-12-01 17:21:24', '2024-12-01 17:21:24', '11'),
(8, 172, 7, NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p><p>Travelers are suggested to carry the following item,</p><ul><li>Personal clothing</li><li>Towel/Gamcha</li><li>Sunglass</li><li>Hat</li><li>Personal Medicine</li><li>Personal Hygiene Products</li><li>Camera with extra battery</li><li>A copy of NID Card</li><li>Dry Food</li><li>Mosquito repellent lotion/cream</li><li>Sunscreen</li><li>Flashlight/Torch Light</li><li>Power Bank</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/6ogXbSjCVkI9XCkz2weZoXKJwEJZRXMqiTd00leK.jpg', 1, 9, '2024-12-01 17:22:41', '2024-12-01 17:22:41', '10'),
