(94, 181, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Experience the beauty of the majestic Tanguar Haor- in the most premium and comfortable way. Live in a luxurious boat to peacefully enjoy the scenic beauty of this majestic Wetland of Sunamganj. Wander around the attractions nearby and get enchanted by the land\'s magic.</p><p><strong>Locations that will be covered in this tour:</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Package Price for Bojra: (Weekday)</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 7,650 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 6,750 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 6,300 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 5,400 Per Person</p><p><strong>Package Price for Bojra: (Weekend)</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 8,500 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 7,000 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 7,500 Per Person<br><br>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 6,000 Per Person</p><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>২</td><td>০</td><td>২</td><td>৫</td></tr><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td><p>জুন</p><p>&nbsp;</p></td><td>&nbsp;</td><td>&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> জুন মাস থেকে&nbsp;</strong><br><br><i><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ১২০০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৯৬০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ২ জন)।</strong></i><br>&nbsp;</p><p><i><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ১০৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৮৪০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ৩ জন)।</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ৯৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৭৬০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ৪ জন)।</strong></i><br>&nbsp;</p><p><i><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ৭৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৬০০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ৮ জন)।</strong></i