(106, 182, 5, 'Description', '<p><strong>Day 1</strong></p><ul><li>Morning: Welcome drinks, cake/light snacks, biscuits, tea</li><li>Breakfast: Khichuri (a rice and lentil dish), beef/mutton/chicken, dried fish mash, egg, pickle, fried eggplant, salad</li><li>Morning Snacks: Tea and biscuits, Light snacks or fruits</li><li>Lunch: One fish curry, one fish mash, one fried fish, fish muri ghonto (a Bengali dish), salad, dal (lentil), coke</li><li>Evening Snacks: Muri and chanachur, Tea</li><li>Dinner: Fried fish, chicken curry, shrimp and vegetables, mash, dal, coke, salad</li></ul><p><strong>Day 2</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Breakfast:</strong>Khichuri, beef/mutton/chicken, dried fish mash, egg, pickle, fried eggplant, salad</li><li><strong>Snacks: </strong>Tea and biscuits, Light snacks or fruits.</li><li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Duck curry, fried fish, panchmisali mach/fish mash, potato mash/vegetables, dal, coke</li><li><strong>Evening Snacks: </strong>Noodles, tea</li></ul>', 'facility_images/t8BhsWNYnnBToY4OtwgdrjOt0tVHML5XGhOtPRMY.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 04:29:14', '2025-03-04 04:29:14', '19'),
(107, 182, 6, 'Additional information', '<p>Information about the Boat: Doheem</p><p>This boat is one of the finest boats of Tanguar Haor that provides professional tourist service. This wooden boat does not get heated up during scorching sun or daytime.</p><ul><li>30 people can be accommodated inside the boat</li><li>This boat has a 130-watt solar panel</li><li>Air Conditioned Cabins</li><li>Total 10 cabins</li><li>This boat has a water filter to store 300 liters of fresh water for regular use.</li><li>Twenty life vests / Life jackets</li><li>Private cook</li><li>Power sockets (charging facility)</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Things to keep in mind</strong></p><ul><li>An adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.</li><li>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.</li><li>The times mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather conditions, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers, and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstances.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li><li>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitants. Travelers are asked to seek help from the tour operator/host/organizer in case they need to contact any local people.</li><li>There is no separate dining space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>In the case of a group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to Lakmachora on a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/OR8Dw1QwW2YJtfP9R0DHKTWVrHPN2Cq6hfVY87R4.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 04:30:08', '2025-03-04 04:30:08', '16'),
(108, 182, 7, 'Travel tips', '<p>Travelers are suggested to carry the following item:</p><ul><li>Personal clothing</li><li>Towel/Gamcha</li><li>Sunglass</li><li>Hat</li><li>Personal Medicine</li><li>Personal Hygiene Products</li><li>Camera with extra battery</li><li>A copy of NID Card</li></ul>', 'facility_images/uNgC6Q4xAkhWfX9OXEDUDe2DLQTFXXSdRRpdGV3C.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 04:31:03', '2025-03-04 04:31:03', '16'),
(109, 203, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Enjoy a traditional Tanguar Haor experience most classically. Stay in a wooden boat for two days and get immersed in the majestic beauty of this popular Wetland of Sunamganj. Explore the scenic beauty of the land and get enchanted by the magical attractions nearby. This tour is ideal for travelers who want to explore Tanguar haor.</p><p><strong>Locations that will be covered in this tour:</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Package Price for Sindabad Tori:</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 8,500 Per Person &nbsp;(Weekend 9500 tk)</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 7,000 Per Person (Weekend 8000 tk)</p><p>Family Cabin -&nbsp;Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 7,000 Per Person &nbsp;(Weekend 8000 tk)</p><p>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 5,500 Per Person &nbsp;(Weekend 6500 tk)</p><p>4500 per person if you want to stay in the lobby. (Weekend 5000 tk)</p><p><strong>Whole Boat Reserved price for Sindabad Tori:</strong></p><p>For 20 persons or more BDT 8,000 Per person</p><p>For 16 persons or more BDT 9,000 Per person</p><p>For 12 persons or more BDT 11,000 Per person</p><p>For 10 persons or more BDT 12,500 Per person</p><p><strong>Special Note: If there are less than 10 people, it should be discussed</strong></p>', 'facility_images/O9RyxEyRK77zxMqyW9vY4ALGry8pjbPRK7SJVUXx.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 04:49:59', '2025-05-13 07:49:39', '16'),
