(112, 203, 5, 'Description', '<p>Located in north-eastern Bangladesh, Tanguar haor is a river basin and a unique wetland ecosystem of national importance. The tour is ideal for you if you want to experience both adventures and serenity. You’ll have a traditional wooden boat with the necessary amenities as your home during the tour. During the tour, you’ll have mouth-watering delicacies more than three times a day while watching the beauty of the wetland from your wooden boathouse. The tour will also let you explore the picturesque beauty of Shimul Bagan, bathe in the mirror-like clear water, visit the popular lakes, and enjoy the view of the hills around. And to fill up your soul, the tour will also have arrangements of live local musical sessions. Hence, the tour will give you both tranquility to your soul and stories to tell.</p><p>Places that will be covered in this tour are</p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li><li>Shonir Haor</li><li>House of Hason Raja</li></ul>', 'facility_images/v7ZahpcYgVkAAw4D60jZPO0e7JO3qgg46UIudgt1.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 04:52:29', '2025-03-04 04:52:29', '15'),
