ve their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>In case of group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to lakmachora in a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/hF2GluuFnz5dAJ0jkKrWTAfaxXOrMDCJPVie1LNP.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 04:53:18', '2025-03-04 04:53:18', '15'),
