(136, 225, 5, 'Description', '<p>Food Menu</p><p>�প্রথম দিন<br>�ওয়েলকাম ড্রিংকসঃ লেবু শরবত<br>�স্ন্যাক্সসঃ<br>কুকিজ/ স্লাইসড কেক,সেদ্ধ ডিম,কলা।<br>�চা/কফি �<br>�ফ্রুটস প্লেট</p><p>�হাওড়ে গোসলের পরঃ<br>স্পেশাল চা �</p><p>�দুপুরের খাবারঃ�<br>মাছ ভুনা, মুরগী ভুনা, মাছ ভর্তা, মাছের মাথা লাউ &nbsp;/ লাউ চিংড়ি, করলা/ ঢেড়স/ মিষ্টি কুমড়া ভাজি<br>ডাল, সালাদ, সফট ড্রিংস , বিশুদ্ধ পানি।</p><p>�বিকেলের স্ন্যাক্সসঃ�<br>ফ্রেঞ্চ ফ্রাই/ সেন্ডউইচ, &nbsp;কফি, বিশুদ্ধ পানি</p><p>�রাতের খাবারঃ�<br>চিকেন বার্বিকিউ, ফিশ ফ্রাই, ডাল দিয়ে লটপটি,পরাটা/লুচি, স্পেশাল সালাদ, মিষ্টি,</p><p>�চা/কফি, মিনারেল পানি �</p><p>�দ্বিতীয় দিন<br>প্রি ব্রেকফাস্টঃ<br>চা, বিস্কুট, কলা।</p><p>�সকালের নাস্তা<br>খিচুড়ি, শুটকি ভর্তা, চিকেন ঝাল কারি, আচার, সালাদ</p><p>�চা/কফি, &nbsp;মিনারেল পানি</p><p>�স্ন্যাকসঃ<br>সিঙ্গারা/ মুড়ি চানাচুর, বিস্কুট, চা/কফি, বিশুদ্ধ পানি</p><p>ফ্রুটস প্লেট</p><p>�দুপুরের খাবারঃ<br>প্লেইন রাইস, হাঁস , মাছ ভাজা, ভর্তা, ঢেড়স ভাজি, ডাল, &nbsp;সালাদ, ২০ লিটার জারের বিশুদ্ধ পানি</p><p><br>আর দারুণ সব কমফোর্ট &nbsp;ফিচার পাবেন একই ছাদের নীচে।<br>দ্রষ্টব্যঃ কাঁচামালের প্রাপ্যতার উপরে খাবারের মেন্যুতে ঈষৎ পরিবর্তন হতে পারে।&nbsp;<br>�কোন স্পেশাল খাবারের রিকোয়ারমেন্ট থাকলে ট্রিপের পূর্বে যোগাযোগ করে নেবার অনুরোধ করা যাচ্ছে।</p><p><br>দ্রষ্টব্যঃ কাঁচামালের প্রাপ্যতার উপরে খাবারের মেন্যুতে ঈষৎ পরিবর্তন হতে পারে।</p>', 'facility_images/dw5Zs4EG9Q2TUQceMEW5sbaCWW897LMCKaxNqdVF.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 07:10:34', '2025-05-13 04:32:22', '17'),
(137, 225, 6, 'Additional information', '<p><strong>Information about the Boat: Joler Gaan</strong></p><p>Eco-Friendly Deluxe Houseboat: Made of wood, it measures 88 feet in length and 18 feet in width.</p><p>Longest and Most Attractive Lobby<strong>: </strong>It has the longest lobby in the Haor region, measuring 225 square feet.</p><p>Total of 8 Lockable Cabins:<strong> </strong>Out of which 6 cabins have attached bathrooms (high commode) with private balconies for enjoying the rain.</p><p>Modern Interiors in Each Room: Equipped with king-size beds (7/6 feet), lights, fans, dressing tables, and mobile charging facilities.</p><p>Amenities Provided:<strong> </strong>Water bottles, towels, soap, imported toothpaste, brushes, shampoo, and lotion.</p><p>Modern Bathroom Features.</p><p>Corridor: 3 feet wide and 7 feet high, allowing easy movement for everyone.</p><p>Rooftop Garden and Dining Area: With comfortable seating arrangements for socializing.</p><p>Electricity Facilities.</p><p>Safety Equipment: Life jackets, buoys, fire extinguishers, and a first aid box.</p><p>Indoor Game Materials: Playing cards, Uno, Ludo, chess, carrom board, etc.</p><p>Prayer Mat for Prayers.</p><p>Modern Kitchen Room.</p><p>Things to keep in mind</p><ul><li>An adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.</li><li>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.</li><li>The times mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather conditions, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers, and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstances.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li><li>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitants. Travelers are asked to seek help from the tour operator/host/organizer in case they need to contact any local people.</li><li>There is no separate dining space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>In the case of a group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to Lakmachora on a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/V6q2tifAbMtN9Tm3cX0uAQpAwwrpgYaxlGI2z4ip.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 07:11:04', '2025-03-04 07:11:04', '19'),
(138, 225, 7, 'Travel tips', '<p>Travelers are suggested to carry the following item:</p><ul><li>Personal clothing</li><li>Towel/Gamcha</li><li>Sunglass</li><li>Hat</li><li>Personal Medicine</li><li>Personal Hygiene Products</li><li>Camera with extra battery</li><li>A copy of NID Card</li></ul>', 'facility_images/Rw03ttf96N6XxcJ8SMbAmuOh91whaNUyr6W221Gk.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 07:11:24', '2025-03-04 07:11:24', '20'),
(139, 225, 13, 'Policy', '<p>Cancellation* &nbsp;<br>To cancel any tour, an email has to be sent to *bookmebdltd@gmail.com* mentioning the tour booking ID, phone number and details about the cancellation. &nbsp;<br>Travelers are responsible for notifying Bookme of any cancellations as soon as possible. &nbsp;<br>The email acts as the final application for cancellation. Phone calls to Bookme\'s hotline or contacting any team member directly will not be considered as cancellation requests. &nbsp;<br>The time of sending the email will be considered as the time of cancellation. &nbsp;<br>In cases of exceptional circumstances, such as acts of God, natural disasters, or mandatory government closures, Bookme may offer alternative dates for the tour or a full refund, at Bookme\'s discretion. &nbsp;<br>If a tour is cancelled by the tour operator due to unforeseen circumstances, travelers will be entitled to a full refund of the tour fee. &nbsp;<br>This policy is subject to change without prior notice. Please refer to the website or booking confirmation voucher/invoice for the most up-to-date information. &nbsp;<br>Tours booked for blackout dates, government holidays, and festival periods are non-refundable and non-cancellable. &nbsp;<br>This cancellation policy may not be applicable in case of national emergency/ lockdown/ political unrest/ natural disaster etc. &nbsp;<br>This policy is applicable to all tour cancellations, regardless of the reason for cancellation.</p><p>*Refund* &nbsp;<br>80% of the fees will be refunded if the booking is canceled more than Twenty-One (21) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>50% of the fees will be refunded if the booking is canceled within Fourteen (14) to Twenty-One (21) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>30% of the tour fee will be refunded if the booking is canceled within Seven (7) to Fourteen (14) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>Refund will not be provided if the tour is cancelled less than Seven (7) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>Convenience fees and insurance fees are non-refundable and will be deducted from the paid amount. &nbsp;<br>All refunds will be processed within seven (7) working days.</p><p>*Child Policy* &nbsp;<br>No fee will be needed for children below the age of three (3). No separate seat will be provided in case of transportation and accommodation. &nbsp;<br>75% fee must be paid for any child between the age of four (4) and ten (10) years old. &nbsp;<br>Full amount of money must be paid for anyone above ten (10) years old.</p>', 'facility_images/s1nZ4JQInksIqHjsKwIqIuuZGNjAMJ3AAjyOjWYj.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 07:11:57', '2025-03-04 07:11:57', '14'),
(143, 206, 4, 'inclusion', '<ul><li>✔All the facilities of the boat<br>✔Private Cook<br>✔Breakfast - Days 1 and 2<br>✔Lunch - Days 1 and 2<br>✔Dinner - Days 1<br>✔Snacks Day 1 and 2<br>✔Life Vests</li><li>✕Dhaka - Sunamganj - Dhaka Non Bus Transportation<br>✕Any personal expenses<br>✕Anything that is not mentioned in the inclusions.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/nGvJLaPilKYTmF6sE5yZSPXxbUVpdX16mgWO0nD7.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 07:29:25', '2025-03-04 07:29:25', '18');
