(159, 200, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Enjoy a traditional Tanguar Haor experience most classically. Stay in a wooden boat for two days and get immersed in the majestic beauty of this popular Wetland of Sunamganj. Explore the scenic beauty of the land and get enchanted by the magical attractions nearby. This tour is ideal for travelers who want to explore Tanguar haor. Write it another way.</p><p>Locations that will be covered in this tour:</p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Hijol Bon</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Package Price for Hijol:</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 9,000 Per Person (weekend 10500 tk)</p><p>Family Cabin - Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 7,500 Per Person (weekend 9000 tk)</p><p>Couple Cabin - Semi Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 7,500 Per Person (weekend 9000 tk)</p><p>4500 per person if you want to stay in the lobby.(weekend 5500 tk)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Till June 5th 20% Discount Available</strong></p>', 'facility_images/jBBoOJgj7TntRWttvwOj1ygkEganeZujQGIipyJj.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-04 08:18:06', '2025-05-13 07:14:15', '16'),
