(254, 238, 4, 'inclusion', '<ul><li>✔Sightseeing<br>✔Welcome drinks<br>✔Accommodation in cabins<br>✔Breakfast (Day 1 and 2)<br>✔Morning Snacks (Day 1 and 2)<br>✔Lunch (Day 1 and 2)<br>✔Evening Snacks (Day 1 and 2)<br>✔Dinner (Day 1)<br>✔Toiletries Items<br>✔Light, Fan and Charging point in each cabin</li><li>✕Transportation to/from Sunamganj<br>✕Any type of personal expenses<br>✕Anything which is not mentioned in the inclusions.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/xyigUOiRrg65Rxf33THUBbSUhj6T5eMv4hVi239Y.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 05:19:32', '2025-03-06 05:19:32', '14'),
(255, 238, 5, 'Description', '<p>Tanguar Haor is a river basin and a unique wetland ecosystem of national importance. If you want to experience the beauty of the land comfortably and lavishly, then the tour is the best match for you. You’ll have a premium wooden boat with extremely comfortable amenities as your home during the tour. The spacious boat will let you wander around within it. During the tour, you’ll have mouth-watering delicacies more than three times a day while watching the beauty of the wetland from your wooden boathouse. The tour will also let you explore the picturesque beauty of Shimul Bagan, bathe in the mirror-like clear water, visit the popular lakes, and enjoy the view of the hills around. And to fill up your soul, the tour will also have arrangements of live local musical sessions. Hence, the tour will give you both tranquility to your soul and stories to tell.</p><p>Places that will be covered in this tour are</p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor watch tower</li><li>Hijol - karac Forest / Submerged Forest</li><li>Jadu Kata river</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake/ Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p>Food Menu</p><p>Day 1</p><ul><li>Breakfast: Bread, Butter, Jelly, Boiled Egg, Banana, Tea &amp; Water. <strong>OR </strong>Bhuna Khichuri,&nbsp;Egg curry, Green Salad, Achar, Tea, Water.&nbsp;</li><li>Morning Snacks: Biscuit/Noodles/Murimakha, Tea &amp; Water</li><li>Lunch: Plain Rice, Bhorta/ vegetable, Fish curry, chicken roast/curry, daal and water.</li><li>Evening Snacks: Biscuit/Noodles /Murimakha Tea &amp; Water</li><li>Dinner: Plain Rice, Duck Curry, Soft Drinks, Water.</li></ul><p>Day 2</p><ul><li>Breakfast: Bread, Butter, Jelly, Boiled Egg, Banana, Tea &amp; Water. <strong>OR</strong> Bhuna Khichuri,&nbsp;Egg curry, Green Salad, Achar, Tea, Water.&nbsp;</li><li>Morning Snacks: Biscuit/Noodles/Murimakha, Tea &amp; Water</li><li>Lunch: Plain rice, Bhorta/vegetable, fish curry, chicken roast/curry, daal, Water.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/xxOTUNsoPEkmTO1HRUloCUUbvc8kAV2YlyaA16AP.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 05:20:08', '2025-03-06 05:20:08', '14');
