(256, 238, 6, 'Additional information', '<p><strong>Information about the Boat: Black Pearl</strong></p><p>This boat is one of the most luxurious boats of Tanguar haor. This is a boat is made with mahogany wood so the boat does not heat up during daytime.</p><ul><li>Six Separate cabins</li><li>Common space</li><li>Rooftop premium dining</li><li>Roof garden</li><li>Juice Bar</li><li>Kitchen</li><li>Two separate toilets (European and Indian style commode)</li><li>Life Vests / Life Jackets</li><li>Lifebuoys</li><li>Power Generator</li><li>Solar Panel</li><li>Every cabins have power sockets and a fan</li><li>Fire Extinguisher</li><li>Experienced Boat Driver</li><li>Professional cook and catering service</li><li>Continuous availability of Tea/Coffee</li><li>Experienced Tour Guide</li></ul><p>Things to keep in mind</p><ul><li>Adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.</li><li>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.</li><li>The time mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to water condition, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstance.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li><li>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitant. Travelers are asked to seek help from tour operator/host/organizer incase they need to contact with any local people.</li><li>There is no separate dinning space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>This is a group tour. There will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to lakmachora in a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/LTo8tJtL7F1psyG5cPqce3DwvShMv556noIjMCUC.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 05:20:49', '2025-03-06 05:20:49', '12'),
(257, 238, 7, 'Travel tips', '<ul><li>Must carry drinking water, stay hydrated, travel healthy.</li><li>Carry a set of fresh clothing for the beach.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/vCVeoTxaCcxTerzBjve5HS1u95lg7f4ZZZP6tmd1.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 05:21:05', '2025-03-06 05:21:05', '14'),
(258, 238, 13, 'Policy', '<p>Cancellation* &nbsp;<br>To cancel any tour, an email has to be sent to *bookmebdltd@gmail.com* mentioning the tour booking ID, phone number and details about the cancellation. &nbsp;<br>Travelers are responsible for notifying Bookme of any cancellations as soon as possible. &nbsp;<br>The email acts as the final application for cancellation. Phone calls to Bookme\'s hotline or contacting any team member directly will not be considered as cancellation requests. &nbsp;<br>The time of sending the email will be considered as the time of cancellation. &nbsp;<br>In cases of exceptional circumstances, such as acts of God, natural disasters, or mandatory government closures, Bookme may offer alternative dates for the tour or a full refund, at Bookme\'s discretion. &nbsp;<br>If a tour is cancelled by the tour operator due to unforeseen circumstances, travelers will be entitled to a full refund of the tour fee. &nbsp;<br>This policy is subject to change without prior notice. Please refer to the website or booking confirmation voucher/invoice for the most up-to-date information. &nbsp;<br>Tours booked for blackout dates, government holidays, and festival periods are non-refundable and non-cancellable. &nbsp;<br>This cancellation policy may not be applicable in case of national emergency/ lockdown/ political unrest/ natural disaster etc. &nbsp;<br>This policy is applicable to all tour cancellations, regardless of the reason for cancellation.</p><p>*Refund* &nbsp;<br>80% of the fees will be refunded if the booking is canceled more than Twenty-One (21) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>50% of the fees will be refunded if the booking is canceled within Fourteen (14) to Twenty-One (21) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>30% of the tour fee will be refunded if the booking is canceled within Seven (7) to Fourteen (14) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>Refund will not be provided if the tour is cancelled less than Seven (7) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>Convenience fees and insurance fees are non-refundable and will be deducted from the paid amount. &nbsp;<br>All refunds will be processed within seven (7) working days.</p><p>*Child Policy* &nbsp;<br>No fee will be needed for children below the age of three (3). No separate seat will be provided in case of transportation and accommodation. &nbsp;<br>75% fee must be paid for any child between the age of four (4) and ten (10) years old. &nbsp;<br>Full amount of money must be paid for anyone above ten (10) years old.</p>', 'facility_images/zSP1Mu9cRfnJJnNdeopi7Hqbwt4Mw9gIVkI6QWFK.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 05:21:25', '2025-03-06 05:21:25', '16'),
(259, 239, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Enjoy a traditional Tanguar Haor experience in the most classical way. Stay in a wooden boat for two days and get immersed in the majestic beauty of this popular Wetland of Sunamganj. Explore the scenic beauty of the land and get enchanted by the magical attractions nearby. This tour is an ideal option for travelers who want to explore tanguar haor.</p><p><strong>Places that will be covered in this tour are:</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor watch tower</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake/ Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Lakma Chhora</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Jadu Kata river</li><li>Hijol - karac Forest / Submerged Forest</li><li>Teker Ghat</li></ul><p><strong>Package Price for La Casa Barco:</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 7,650 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 6,750 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 6,300 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 5,400 Per Person<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; জুন মাস থেকে</strong><br><br><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ১২০০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৯৬০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ২ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ১০৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৮৪০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ৩ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ৯৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৭৬০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ৪ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দা ৭৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৬০০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ৮ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>এটাচ বাথ &nbsp;১০৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৮৪০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ২ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>নন-এটাচ বাথ &nbsp;৯৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৭৬০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ২ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>নন-এটাচ বাথ &nbsp;৭৫০০/- ২০% ডিস্কাউন্ট ৬০০০/- জনপ্রতি ( ২ জন)।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;<