(267, 240, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Discover the timeless charm of Tanguar Haor with a classic two-day adventure. Begin your journey as you step aboard a beautifully crafted wooden boat, guided by experienced local boatmen. Cruise through the serene waters mirroring the vast sky above, immersing yourself in a voyage steeped in tradition that showcases the harmonious relationship between the land and its inhabitants. As you drift through the untouched wetlands, you\'ll be captivated by the dance of light and water, surrounded by lush landscapes and captivating nearby attractions that exude an untarnished sense of wonder. This traditional excursion not only allows you to deeply connect with nature but also offers a glimpse into the rich cultural fabric of the region, making it the perfect escape for those in search of an authentic exploration of Tanguar Haor\'s enchanting beauty.</p><p><strong>Places that will be covered in this tour are:</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor watch tower</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake/ Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Lakma Chhora</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Jadu Kata river</li><li>Hijol - karac Forest / Submerged Forest</li><li>Teker Ghat</li></ul>', 'facility_images/pJ6OnEJn8ZjXnzzA2zHGQtQfId5gBX95n1cM5qeL.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 05:56:39', '2025-03-06 05:56:39', '13'),
