(275, 241, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Enjoy a traditional Tanguar Haor experience most classically. Stay in a wooden boat for two days and get immersed in the majestic beauty of this popular Wetland of Sunamganj. Explore the scenic beauty of the land and get enchanted by the magical attractions nearby. This tour is ideal for travelers who want to explore Tanguar haor.</p><p>Locations that will be covered in this tour:</p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Package Price for Gangchil:</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 7,500 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 6,500 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 6,000 Per Person</p><p>4,500 per person if you want to stay in the lobby</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; 18% to 25% off for group tour&nbsp;<br>weekend 116000-18%= BDT 95120<br>week days 116000-25%=BDT 87000&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/lmdSxlhzbFCGZ5ITnVWGX6WZySJF02dNiCcuK3iL.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 06:39:43', '2025-05-28 06:20:17', '16'),
(276, 241, 3, 'Location', '<p><strong>Pick-up আনোয়ার পুর</strong></p><p><strong>Around: </strong>Tanguar Haor, Watch Tower, Jadukata River, Barikka Tila, Teker Ghat, Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake, Khorchar Haor, Shonir Haor House of Hason Raja, Sunamganj City.</p>', 'facility_images/nN7vTiacJK9fYMdqn7V1rDai5Be8GwgZT2wRSBuH.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 06:40:02', '2025-05-28 06:28:46', '17'),
