(278, 241, 4, 'inclusion', '<ul><li>✔All the facilities of the boat<br>✔Private Cook<br>✔Welcome Drink<br>✔Breakfast - Days 1 and 2<br>✔Lunch - Days 1 and 2<br>✔Dinner - Day 1<br>✔Snacks Day 1 and 2<br>✔Life Vests</li><li>✕Dhaka - Sunamganj - Dhaka Non Ac Bus Transportation (For Group Tour only)<br>✕Any personal expenses<br>✕Shimul Bagan entry fee<br>✕Bike ride fee<br>✕Anything that is not mentioned in the inclusions.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/dAvwpUH9KhbgZONOMh45Glffwg02HL7unyveN8VC.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 06:40:42', '2025-03-06 06:40:42', '20'),
(279, 241, 5, 'Description', '<p>Located in north-eastern Bangladesh, Tanguar haor is a river basin and a unique wetland ecosystem of national importance. The tour is ideal for you if you want to experience both adventures and serenity. You’ll have a traditional wooden boat with the necessary amenities as your home during the tour. During the tour, you’ll have mouth-watering delicacies more than three times a day while watching the beauty of the wetland from your wooden boathouse. The tour will also let you explore the picturesque beauty of Shimul Bagan, bathe in the mirror-like clear water, visit the popular lakes, and enjoy the view of the hills around. And to fill up your soul, the tour will also have arrangements of live local musical sessions. Hence, the tour will give you both tranquility to your soul and stories to tell.</p><p>Places that will be covered in this tour are</p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li><li>Shonir Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Food Menu:</strong></p><p><strong>Day - 1</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Khichuri, Egg Curry, Salad, Mashed Onion, Tea.</li><li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Singara, Tea.</li><li><strong>Lunch: </strong>Steamed Rice, Fish, Chicken Curry, Mashed Potato/ Spinach, Vegatable, Daal, Salad, Tea.</li><li><strong>Afternoon Snacks:</strong> Halim/ Biscuits, Tea.</li><li><strong>Dinner: </strong>Steamed Rice, Duck, Fish, Dried Fish , Vegetables, Daal, Salad</li></ul><p><strong>Day - 2</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Snacks: </strong>Tea, Puffed Rice</li><li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Luchi, Mug Daal, Halua, Tea</li><li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Murimakha, Tea.</li><li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Polao, Roast, Fish Fry, Fried Potato, Bhorta, Murighanta, Payesh.</li><li><strong>Afternoon Snacks:</strong> Vegetables Roll, Tea</li></ul>', 'facility_images/DQE9Logv7eckjuYD1T0TNt65Xd8cZDQ1wTItdOTu.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 06:41:04', '2025-03-06 06:41:04', '17'),
(280, 241, 6, 'Additional information', '<p>Things to keep in mind</p><ul><li>Adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.</li><li>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.</li><li>The time mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather condition, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstance.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li><li>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitant. Travelers are asked to seek help from tour operator/host/organizer incase they need to contact with any local people.</li><li>There is no separate dinning space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>In case of group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to lakmachora in a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/bqlT9tnBEjWBNnC83u1782fxb9t2KKbl0yV0YLhe.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 06:41:28', '2025-03-06 06:41:28', '21'),
