(292, 243, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Enjoy a traditional Tanguar Haor experience in the most classical way. Stay in a wooden boat for two days and get immersed in the majestic beauty of this popular Wetland of Sunamganj. Explore the scenic beauty of the land and get enchanted by the magical attractions nearby. This tour is ideal for travelers who want to explore Tanguar haor.</p><p><strong>Places that will be covered in this tour are</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor watch tower</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake/ Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Lakma Chhora</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Jadu Kata river</li><li>Hijol - karac Forest / Submerged Forest</li><li>Teker Ghat</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Rajar Tori Elite&nbsp;</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Full Boat at Holiday 120000 tk (18 to 20 person), 110500 (15 to 17 person), 94000 tk (12 to 14 person), 90000 tk (8 to 9 person)<br><br>Full Boat at Week Days 100000 tk (18 to 20 person), 93500 tk (15 to 17 person), 91000 tk (12 to 14 person), 80000 tk (8 to 9 person)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sharing Package&nbsp;<br>Lock Door Cabin weekend&nbsp;</p><p>Non Attach Bathroom for 2 person 6500 tk per person (weekdays 6000 tk)</p><p>Non Attach Bathroom for 3 person 6000 tk per person (weekdays 5000 tk)<br>Attach Bathroom for 2 person 7000 tk per person (weekdays 6500 tk)</p><p>Attach Bathroom for 3 person 6500 tk per person (weekdays 6000 tk)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Rajar Tori Family</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Full Boat at weekdays 4000 tk per person (13 to 14 person), 4500 tk per person (11 to 12 person), 5000 tk per person (9 to 10 person), 6000 tk per person (7 to 8 person),<br><br>Full Boat at Holiday 63000 tk (13 to 14person), 60000 tk (11 to 12 person), 55000 tk (9to 10 person), 48000 tk (7 to 8 person)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/14cOLRP0dg53ybIMIm6szEG1Y3YH5hTDTXI8GDTU.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 07:09:27', '2025-05-13 08:23:51', '15'),
