(320, 246, 5, 'Description', '<p><strong>Day 1</strong></p><ul><li>Breakfast: Chicken Akhni, Salad, Tea.</li><li>Snacks: Seasonal Fruits, Tea.</li><li>Lunch: Rice, Bhorta, Vegetables, Chicken Curry, Daal, Drinking Water, Dessert</li><li>Afternoon Snacks: Noodles, Tea/ Biscuits, Tea.</li><li>Dinner: Rice, Fish Bhorta, Duck Bhuna, Daal, Sweets, Soft Drinks.</li></ul><p><strong>Day 2</strong></p><ul><li>Breakfast:Khichuri, Egg Vaja, Pickles, Salad, Tea.</li><li>Snacks: Local Fruits,Tea/ Singara, Tea.</li><li>Lunch: Rice, Bhorta, Fish, Chicken Curry, Salad, Drinking Water.</li><li>Evening Snacks: Murimakha/ Noodles, Tea/ Pasta, Tea,/ Seasonal Fruits, Tea.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/YeMYGgFWQCpVzU60EaAdoBU1ep81fVIznQH15o0h.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-06 08:05:02', '2025-03-06 08:05:02', '19'),
