(343, 252, 4, 'inclusion', '<ul><li>✔Two nights’ accommodation on a Single/Double/Twin/Triple bed-sharing cabin<br>✔All meals during the trip<br>✔All activities inside the forest as per itinerary<br>✔Mineral water for drinking during the trip<br>✔Forest fees &amp; permission (for Bangladeshi nationals only)<br>✔Armed forest guard from the forest department<br>✔An experienced tour Guide<br>✔All-time Tea, Coffee, and drinking water in the lounge room.<br>✔Country boat cruise inside the forest<br>✔All applicable taxes and tolls</li><li>✕Bus, train or any other transportation to Khulna<br>✕Beverages / Drinks - Hard &amp; Soft.<br>✕Items of personal nature - Postage, Phone, Fax, Internet, Medicine, Insurance, Laundry, etc.<br>✕Tips to Guide &amp; Driver.<br>✕Anything that is not mentioned in the inclusions</li></ul>', 'facility_images/5IqIyy6tV2RSFA3w5KFIHMEsweOiMOySHGiHy9f2.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-22 05:34:00', '2025-03-22 05:34:00', '15'),
(344, 252, 5, 'Description', '<p>Sundarbans is the largest mangrove forest in the world and a natural world heritage listed by UNESCO. This mangrove forest hosts an amazing faunal &amp; floral diversity, including the probably largest remaining population of Royal Bengal tigers, the endangered estuarine crocodile, Ganges River dolphins as well as an astounding variety of birds. Join our luxurious cruise and explore this intricate maze of tidal waterways, a natural treasure of Bangladesh.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>FOOD MENU :&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1st Day:</strong></p><p><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Paratha, Vegetables, Mug Dal bhuna, Egg fry, tea/Coffee.</p><p><strong>Morning Snacks:</strong> Fruit cake, tea/coffee.</p><p><strong>Lunch:</strong> White rice, green prawns, vetki fish (coral), duck meat bharta, dal, Sweets, Salad.</p><p><strong>Evening Snacks:</strong> French Fry &amp; Soup.</p><p><strong>Dinner:</strong> Egg fried rice, chicken fry, fried shrimp, Chinese vegetables, salad, soft drinks.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2nd Day:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Bhuna khichuri, sea fish, brinjal vaji, egg curry, pickles, salad, tea/coffee.</p><p><strong>Morning Snacks:</strong> Sarabat, Guava, Tea/Coffee</p><p><strong>Lunch:</strong> White rice, bharta, gourd prawns, chicken curry, dal, salad, dessert.</p><p><strong>Evening Snacks:</strong> Puri/Pakura, tea/coffee.</p><p><strong>Dinner:</strong> Porata, Chicken Bar-b-fish Bar-b-q, Booter Dal Buna, Russian Salad, Cold Drinks.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3rd Day:</strong></p><p><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Paratha, vegetables, Gorur kolija bhuna, Shuji halwa, tea/coffee.</p><p><strong>Morning Snacks:</strong> Fruit, tea/coffee.</p><p><strong>Lunch:</strong> Plain rice, Rupchada fish, mutton, vharta, dal salad, Sweet Card</p><p><strong>Evening Snacks:</strong> Nodols &amp;&nbsp;tea/coffee.</p>', 'facility_images/xQiUlJpInf30og6Pc9soQNMXo0tywyr9yEFdzZhD.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-22 05:45:38', '2025-03-22 05:45:38', '13'),
