(346, 255, 12, 'List of packages', '<p>Escape to the serene beauty of Cox\'s Bazar, a destination known for its breathtaking sea beaches and stunning mountain views, for a memorable, romantic getaway. This three-day, two-night retreat offers a perfect blend of relaxation and adventure, making it an ideal holiday for couples seeking tranquillity and a connection with nature.</p><p><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Enchanting Views:</strong> Wake up to mesmerizing views of the world’s longest unbroken sea beach, complemented by the lush mountains surrounding the area.</li><li><strong>Quality Accommodation:</strong> Choose between a cosy 3-star experience or indulge in luxury with a 5-star hotel, both designed to offer comfort and exceptional service.</li><li><strong>Romantic Atmosphere:</strong> Whether you are strolling hand-in-hand along the beach or enjoying a peaceful evening overlooking the horizon, this tour is tailored to create unforgettable memories with your loved one.</li><li><strong>Exciting Experiences:</strong> Explore the local culture, relax on the pristine beaches, or enjoy a peaceful evening at your resort with world-class amenities.</li></ul><p><strong>Package Options: (Ramadan Special)</strong></p><h4><strong>Economy Package (3-Star Hotel):</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Hotel: </strong>Hotel Kollol by J&amp;Z Group, Royal Pearl Suites, Lighthouse Family Retreat/ or similar.</li><li><strong>Starting Price:</strong> BDT 13,999 per person</li><li><strong>Minimum Persons:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Couples seeking an affordable yet romantic and comfortable beach holiday.</li></ul><h4><strong>Premium Package (5-Star Hotel):</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Hotel:</strong> Sayeman Beach Resort, Sayeman Heritage, Sea Pearl Beach Resort &amp; Spa/ or similar.</li><li><strong>Starting Price:</strong> BDT 16,499 per person</li><li><strong>Minimum Persons:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Couples looking for