(353, 258, 4, NULL, '<h4><strong>Overview</strong></h4><p><strong>Overview of the Romantic Cox\'s Bazar Retreat (3 Days, 2 Nights)</strong></p><p>Escape to the serene beauty of Cox\'s Bazar, a destination known for its breathtaking sea beaches and stunning mountain views, for a memorable, romantic getaway. This three-day, two-night retreat offers a perfect blend of relaxation and adventure, making it an ideal holiday for couples seeking tranquillity and a connection with nature.</p><p><strong>Tour Highlights:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Enchanting Views:</strong> Wake up to mesmerizing views of the world’s longest unbroken sea beach, complemented by the lush mountains surrounding the area.</li><li><strong>Quality Accommodation:</strong> Choose between a cosy 3-star experience or indulge in luxury with a 5-star hotel, both designed to offer comfort and exceptional service.</li><li><strong>Romantic Atmosphere:</strong> Whether you are strolling hand-in-hand along the beach or enjoying a peaceful evening overlooking the horizon, this tour is tailored to create unforgettable memories with your loved one.</li><li><strong>Exciting Experiences:</strong> Explore the local culture, relax on the pristine beaches, or enjoy a peaceful evening at your resort with world-class amenities.</li></ul><p><strong>Package Options: (Ramadan Special)</strong></p><h4><strong>Economy Package (3-Star Hotel):</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Hotel: </strong>Hotel Kollol by J&amp;Z Group, Royal Pearl Suites, Lighthouse Family Retreat/ or similar.</li><li><strong>Starting Price:</strong> BDT 13,999 per person</li><li><strong>Minimum Persons:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Couples seeking an affordable yet romantic and comfortable beach holiday.</li></ul><h4><strong>Premium Package (5-Star Hotel):</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Hotel:</strong> Sayeman Beach Resort, Sayeman Heritage, Sea Pearl Beach Resort &amp; Spa/ or similar.</li><li><strong>Starting Price:</strong> BDT 16,499 per person</li><li><strong>Minimum Persons:</strong> 2</li><li><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Couples looking for luxury, privacy, and a lavish stay with top-tier amenities.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/q8P1ojBga2hTOXJY43LxyMDSLBDMn3lGWmw01Hji.jpg', 1, 5, '2025-03-23 09:38:32', '2025-03-23 09:38:32', '17'),
(354, 257, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Embark on a captivating 3-day, 2-night journey into the mesmerizing beauty of the Sundarbans, the world\'s largest mangrove forest. Luxury vessel, MV Alaska Cruise, ensures both safety and indulgence as you explore this natural wonder. Encounter diverse wildlife, from the iconic Royal Bengal tigers to rare estuarine crocodiles and Ganges River dolphins. Sail through tidal waterways, visiting Herbaria, Kochikhali, Dimer Char, Katka, and Karamjal. Indulge in delicious full-board meals while immersing yourself in the Sundarbans\' allure. This is your gateway to a unique Bangladeshi treasure.</p><p><strong>Package Price for MV Alaska Cruise:</strong></p><p><strong>Cabin Type-1:</strong> Couple Cabin - Attached Bath for 2 Travelers</p><p>Price: BDT 22,000 Per Person</p><p><strong>Cabin Type-2:</strong> Family Cabin - Attached Bath for 4 Travelers</p><p>Price: BDT 22,000 Per Person</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Remember, the cost per person is less if you have more people in your group.</p>', 'facility_images/gxgAx6vhfFwCYcV7WIvSZTFm6LSLvpRaNFzXOrBN.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-24 06:24:43', '2025-03-24 06:24:43', '15'),
