(373, 261, 4, NULL, '<ul><li>✔Two nights’ accommodation on a Single/Double/Twin/Triple/Four Bed-sharing cabin<br>✔All meals during the trip<br>✔All activities inside the forest as per the itinerary<br>✔Mineral water for drinking during the trip<br>✔Forest fees &amp; permission (for Bangladeshi nationals only)<br>✔Armed forest guard from the forest department<br>✔An experienced tour Guide<br>✔All-time tea, coffee, and drinking water are available in the lounge room.<br>✔Country boat cruise inside the forest<br>✔All applicable taxes and tolls</li><li>✕Beverages / Drinks - Hard &amp; Soft.<br>✕Items of personal nature - Postage, Phone, Fax, Internet, Medicine, Insurance, Laundry, etc.<br>✕Tips to Guide &amp; Driver.<br>✕Anything that is not mentioned in the inclusions</li></ul>', 'facility_images/liHOIDsvlfvEcpXRRITI3KOXY2nqAKUmgtEZq5zM.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-25 04:02:17', '2025-03-25 04:02:17', '16'),
(374, 261, 5, NULL, '<p>Step into the extraordinary world of the Sundarbans, a sprawling expanse of wonder that stands as the largest mangrove forest on the globe. Its awe-inspiring beauty has earned it a distinguished spot on UNESCO\'s list of natural world heritage sites.</p><p>This enchanting mangrove forest is a sanctuary of unparalleled diversity, where the tapestry of life weaves together in stunning harmony. Here, amidst the intertwining roots and lush greenery, you\'ll find a captivating array of fauna and flora. It\'s home to what is believed to be the largest surviving population of the majestic Royal Bengal tigers, a testament to nature\'s magnificence. The elusive estuarine crocodile, the enchanting Ganges River dolphins, and a myriad of vibrant bird species complete the ensemble of life that calls this forest home.</p><p>Picture yourself aboard our luxurious cruise, an experience that seamlessly blends opulence and discovery. As you navigate this intricate maze of tidal waterways, every twist and turn reveals a new facet of this natural gem nestled within Bangladesh\'s heart. The journey is as much a destination as the forest itself.</p><p>Indulge in the symphony of senses as you explore the diverse ecosystems, from the dense mangrove thickets to the tranquil waterways. With each moment, you\'ll be immersed in the spellbinding allure that the Sundarbans effortlessly casts. And when it\'s time to savor a moment of reprieve, our cruise promises not only comfort but culinary delights, with a tantalizing array of full-board meals to satiate your appetite for both adventure and fine dining.</p><p>This is your chance to be a part of something truly remarkable – a voyage into the heart of a natural treasure, where every glimpse is a glimpse into the timeless rhythm of nature\'s dance. Join us in discovering the Sundarbans, where the extraordinary is simply the ordinary.&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/EyO0MmqclnrCNEfVREZKjFdfGitdp9qruEaf3wec.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-25 04:05:15', '2025-03-25 04:05:15', '18'),
