(386, 275, 12, NULL, '<p>Discover the magnificently mysterious beauty of the Sundarbans, which is home to the largest mangrove forest in the world. The tour lasts for three days and two nights, and it\'s meant to be a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity for guests. Armed guards ensure the safety of the journey from Khulna to the Sundarbans. Nobody else is allowed to bring firearms into the Sundarbans, nor are they permitted to leave them there. Spend the night in the Sundarbans as you go to Kochikhali and Kotka. The area\'s vegetation and fauna can be explored via boat at a dedicated facility. Full board meals on a delicious menu are included in the price of the cruise for the entire itinerary duration. The \"MV Aral Sea\" is widely regarded as one of the most opulent and comfortable air-conditioned cruises available in the Sundarbans. It can accommodate up to sixty visitors.</p><p><strong>Package Price for MV Aral Sea Cruise:</strong></p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> Couple Cabin/ Triple Share- Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 17,000 Per Person</p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> Family Cabin - Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 18,000 Per Person</p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> VIP Couple Cabin - Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 20,000 Per Person</p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> VVIP Couple Cabin - Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 22,000 Per Person</p><p><strong>Tour Highlights-</strong></p><ul><li>Fully air-conditioned ship</li><li>modern furnished rooms</li><li>All attached Bath Cabins</li><li>Air-conditioned dining room</li><li>Multimedia projector</li><li>Digital sound system</li><li>Huge conference facilities</li><li>CCTV monitoring</li><li>Wi-Fi</li><li>State-of-the-art GPS, Radar, Echo Sounder, VSF, 3 Generators Skilled Sailors, Cabin Crew, Special Cook, and Experienced Guides.</li><li>Each tour includes a BBQ dinner.</li></ul><p><strong>Our travel destination:</strong></p><ol><li>Harbaria</li><li>Katka Forest</li><li>Tiger Tila</li><li>Jamtala Beach</li><li>Kochikhali / Hiron Point</li><li>Dimer Char / Dublar Char</li><li>Karamjol</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Remember, the cost per person is less if you have more people in your group.</p>', 'facility_images/rKgN53oDiejqEV8xwbU5tRyXeJ1mQi8ClHJfsiBF.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-25 08:22:34', '2025-03-25 08:22:34', '16'),
