(390, 275, 5, NULL, '<p>Ship Details: MV Aral Sea</p><p><strong>Presidential Suites</strong></p><p><strong>Honeymoon Suites</strong></p><p><strong>Panorama King Suites</strong></p><p><strong>Bridal Suites</strong>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Ultra Deluxe King Suites</strong>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Triple Super Deluxe</strong></p><p><strong>Triple Standards Suites</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Total Accommodation: 56 guests</p><p>All cabins are AC with attached bathrooms having RO filtering, pressure booster hot &amp; cold water supply.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Meal Plan for Sundarban Cruise-</p><p><strong>Day 1:</strong></p><p>Special Welcome Drinks</p><p>Morning: Bread + Butter + Jam + Cornflakes + Milk + Egg Poach + Boiled Egg</p><p>Khalisa Flower Honey + Banana + Malta + Tea/Coffee</p><p>Snacks: Chicken Roll + Apple / Pepe + Tea/Coffee</p><p>Lunch: Basmati Rice + Bharta + Gourd Shrimp + Roop Chanda Fish Dopiaza +</p><p>Chuijhal Beef + Dal + Salad + Cold Drinks + Raso Gol + Frot + Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Snacks: Fish Fries + Hot &amp; Sour Soup + French Fries + Tea/Coffee</p><p>Dinner: Mixed Fried Rice + Sweet and Sour Prawns + Fried Chicken + Chinese Vegetables + Cashew Nut Salad + Foot Custard / Faluda + Cold Drinks + Tea / Coffee.</p><p><strong>Day 2:</strong></p><p>Morning tea: raw cow\'s milk/glucose + dry cake + tea/coffee</p><p>Morning: Bhunakhichuri + Quail Fries + Khasir Kalija Bhuna + Eggplant Fry + Pickle + Green Salad + Jeerapani Drinks + Tea/Coffee</p><p>Snacks: Fruit Juice + Chicken Sandwiches + Guava / Plum + Tea/Coffee</p><p>Lunch: Basmati Rice + Shrimp Bharta + Banana Bharta + Mixed Vegetables + Chicken Curry + Faisa Fish Dopiaza + Dal + Salad + Sarpuria + Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Snacks: Chicken Wins/Nuggets + Potato Wedges + Thai Soup + Tea/Coffee</p><p>Dinner: Butter Naan + Chicken BBQ + Fish BBQ + Mash Potato Vegetable Fries + Russian Salad + Cold Drinks + Special Juice Malai, Tea/Coffee.</p><p><strong>Day -3</strong></p><p>Morning Tea: Cow Milk + Lexus Biscuits + Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Breakfast: Turkish Bread + Roast Beef + Fried Egg + Dal Makhana + Juice Pies + Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Snacks: Beler Sarabat / Lemon Juice + Foot Cake + Mixed Frot + Tea/Coffee Lunch: Pollau + Coral Fish Dopiaza + Chicken Roast + Eggplant Fried Green Salad + Yogurt + Cold Drinks + Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Snacks: Khasi Barbeque + Bosnian Naan + Fried Vegetables + Cold</p><p>Drinks + Tea/Coffee.</p>', 'facility_images/MJZXTyo3xZN63bgRif7ZSYViWfJkTHIjfKEZHRj6.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-25 09:07:13', '2025-03-25 09:07:13', '12'),
