(398, 273, 5, NULL, '<p><strong>MV Sunway</strong> is a modern and luxurious tourist vessel of Sundarbans. All the cabins are fully airconditioned. Some other mentionable facilities of MV Sunway are:</p><ul><li>Luxurious AC cruise ship</li><li>BBQ Corner</li><li>Water reservoir</li><li>Wall with wooden interior decoration</li><li>Separate place for prayer</li><li>Modern Radar and GPS system</li><li>Fire Safety system</li><li>Inhouse Chef and Waiters</li><li>Armed Security Guards</li><li>Travel Guide</li><li>Adequate amount of life jacket and lifebuoys</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Meal Plan for Sundarbans Cruise-</p><p><strong>Day 1:</strong></p><p>Breakfast: Porata,kalija Bhuna, Butter, Halua,Honey ,Egg Omelet,Sweets,Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Snacks: Fruits,Cookies,Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Lunch: Plain Rice, Chicken Fry, Chicken Curry, Sea Fish, Bhorta, Vegetable, Salads, Soft Drinks, Dessert.</p><p>Snacks: Dry Cake/Vegetable Pakora, Tea/Coffee.</p><p>BBQ Dinner:&nbsp;Fried rice, Chicken fry. Shrimp Curry, Chinese Vegetable, Salads, Soft Drinks, Dessert.</p><p><strong>Day 2:</strong></p><p>Breakfast:&nbsp;&nbsp;Khichuri,Chicken Curry,Sour Pickle,Dessert, Tea/ Coffee.</p><p>Snacks: Green Coconut,Fruits/Cookies,Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Lunch: Plain Rice, Sea Fish,Chui Mutton Bhuna,Mixed Vegetable, Dal, Salads.</p><p>Evening Snacks: Soup, French Fries, Tea/Coffee,</p><p>Dinner: Motor Polaw, Parata, Chicken Bar-B-Q, Fish Bar-B-Q, Gravy Vegetable, Bhuna dal,Salads,Soft Drinks,Dessert.</p><p><strong>Day -3</strong></p><p>Breakfast: Porata, Chicken Curry, Dal,Egg Omelet,Tea/Coffee.</p><p>Snacks: Cookies/Fruits,Tea/Coffee</p><p>Lunch: Mutton Biriyani, Egg,Chicken Roast,Sweet Curd,Salads, Soft Drinks.</p>', 'facility_images/65OoEH8ZOJVTPE7AUWnOups5xmWgnDixaCv9gzKg.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-27 07:20:10', '2025-03-27 07:20:10', '17'),
(399, 273, 6, NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Additional charges will be applied as permit fee for foreigner/non Bangladeshi traveler as per government regulation.</strong></li><li>National ID card to be provided on booking.</li><li>All mentioned durations and activities are subject to change depending on tide, weather and safety conditions.</li><li>The tour operator will responsible for the operation of the tours and excursions as mentioned under the normal situation. So, for personal accident, sickness, loss of baggage during the tour, delay or cancellation of air flight, any political problem resulting in an unusual situation to conduct a tour, etc. we shall not be directly responsible. While the tour operator will responsible for extending all possible assistance in overcoming those problems, but the guest must pay any extra cost incurred due to these problems.</li><li>The time mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather condition, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstance.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>No alcohol will be available for sale on board.</li><li>No phone signal works inside the deeper forest. But at some point, you will get a phone signal to call the emergency. If you use Bangladeshi TeleTalk SIM, we’ll get better coverage in a remote area like Kotka.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Must bring National ID card</li><li>Valid permission for drone and professional camera from respective authorities</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/a9qUWJCWRQ2zCgcPLUtdcd28VKi1SpgE6NUzCW1L.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-27 07:21:02', '2025-03-27 07:21:02', '17'),
(400, 272, 12, NULL, '<p>Discover the magnificently mysterious beauty of the Sundarbans, which is home to the largest mangrove forest in the world. The tour lasts for three days and two nights, and it\'s meant to be a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity for guests. Armed guards ensure the safety of the journey from Khulna to the Sundarbans. Nobody else is allowed to bring firearms into the Sundarbans, nor are they permitted to leave them there. Spend the night in the Sundarbans as you go to Kochikhali and Kotka. The area\'s vegetation and fauna can be explored via boat at a dedicated facility. Full board meals on a delicious menu are included in the price of the cruise for the entire itinerary duration. The \"Pirates of the Sundarban\" is widely regarded as one of the most opulent and comfortable air-conditioned cruises available in the Sundarbans. It can accommodate up to sixty visitors.</p><p><strong>Package Price for Pirates of the Sundarban:</strong></p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> Couple Cabin/ Triple Share/ Family Cabin- Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 15,000 Per Person</p><p><strong>Tour Highlights-</strong></p><ul><li>Fully air-conditioned ship</li><li>All cabins have attached washroom</li><li>Grand dining hall with jungle view</li><li>50,000 litter fresh water tank</li><li>24 hours generator service</li><li>Prayer room</li><li>GPS, VHF &amp; Eco sounder - all latest equipment installed</li><li>Fire extinguisher</li><li>Life jacket &amp; lifebuoy for all the crew</li><li>Refrigerated food</li><li>3 types of 14 luxurious cabins</li></ul><p><strong>Our travel destination:</strong></p><ol><li>Andhamanik</li><li>Katka Forest</li><li>Tiger Tila</li><li>Jamtala Beach</li><li>Kochikhali / Hiron Point</li><li>Dimer Char / Dublar Char</li><li>Karamjol</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Remember, the cost per person is less if you have more people in your group.</p>', 'facility_images/4mWJXALukZFN38nrLjokLivrjQXQkHC4mYBvY7q6.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-03-29 06:28:14', '2025-03-29 06:28:14', '13'),
