(428, 277, 5, NULL, '<p>Tanguar Haor is a river basin and a unique wetland ecosystem of national importance. If you want to experience the beauty of the land comfortably and lavishly, then the tour is the best match for you. You’ll have a premium wooden boat with extremely comfortable amenities as your home during the tour. The spacious boat will let you wander around within it. During the tour, you’ll have mouth-watering delicacies more than three times a day while watching the beauty of the wetland from your wooden boathouse. The tour will also let you explore the picturesque beauty of Shimul Bagan, bathe in the mirror-like clear water, visit the popular lakes, and enjoy the view of the hills around. And to fill up your soul, the tour will also have arrangements of live local musical sessions. Hence, the tour will give you both tranquility to your soul and stories to tell.</p><p><strong>Places that will be covered in this tour are</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake/ Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Food Menu</strong></p><p>Day 1</p><ul><li>Breakfast: Khichuri, Egg Omelets, begun bhaja, achar, salad and tea.</li><li>Morning Snacks: Lemon juice and seasonal fruits.</li><li>Lunch: Plain Rice, Chicken curry, vegetables, local fish curry and Daal</li><li>Evening Snacks: Noodles and cold drinks.</li><li>Dinner: Plain Rice, Duck Curry, vegetables, sweets and tea.</li></ul><p>Day 2</p><ul><li>Breakfast: Polau, Egg curry, begun bhaja, achar, salad and tea.</li><li>Morning Snacks: Lemon juice and seasonal fruits.</li><li>Lunch: Plain Rice, Chicken curry, vegetables, local fish curry and Daal</li><li>Evening Snacks: Noodles and tea</li></ul>', 'facility_images/fLwFk0aHDFCfKqYlAGbaEszxuYTXAC1OriUAw5NI.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-06 04:38:04', '2025-04-06 04:38:04', '15'),
(429, 277, 6, NULL, '<p>Bojra (বজরা) - The House Boat</p><p>This boat is one of the most luxurious boats of Tanguar haor. This is a boat is made with mahogany wood so the boat does not heat up during daytime.</p><ul><li>Six Separate cabins</li><li>Common space</li><li>Kitchen</li><li>Two separate toilets (European and Indian style commode)</li><li>One Changing Room</li><li>Twenty Life Vests / Life Jackets</li><li>Two Lifebuoys</li><li>Power Generator</li><li>Solar Panel</li><li>Every cabins have power sockets and a fan</li></ul><p><strong>Things to keep in mind</strong></p><ul><li>Adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.</li><li>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.</li><li>The time mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to water condition, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstance.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li><li>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitant. Travelers are asked to seek help from tour operator/host/organizer incase they need to contact with any local people.</li><li>There is no separate dinning space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>This is a group tour. There will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to lakmachora in a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/sQvAQLSRqi43ejEzDtaxaVjCdG9raqh49wHqHNYT.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-06 04:38:36', '2025-04-06 04:38:36', '17'),
