e tour is cancelled less than Seven (7) days before the beginning of the experience/tour. &nbsp;<br>Convenience fees and insurance fees are non-refundable and will be deducted from the paid amount. &nbsp;<br>All refunds will be processed within seven (7) working days.</p><p>*Child Policy* &nbsp;<br>No fee will be needed for children below the age of three (3). No separate seat will be provided in case of transportation and accommodation. &nbsp;<br>75% fee must be paid for any child between the age of four (4) and ten (10) years old. &nbsp;<br>Full amount of money must be paid for anyone above ten (10) years old.</p>', 'facility_images/fxhe6U0U2DF115FkaRxtN8OWyHlBxEgThHGnwczt.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-06 04:41:16', '2025-04-06 04:41:16', '14'),
(432, 277, 12, NULL, '<p>Experience the beauty of the majestic Tanguar Haor- in the most premium and comfortable way. Live in a luxurious boat to peacefully enjoy the scenic beauty of this majestic Wetland of Sunamganj. Wander around the attractions nearby and get enchanted by the land\'s magic.</p><p><strong>Locations that will be covered in this tour:</strong></p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Shimul Bagan</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li></ul><h2>Khorchar Haor<br><br><strong>Boat Packages Rate for Full Boat</strong></h2><p>Group Size<br>14 - 15 Pax = Raguler Rate 1,28,000 (Discount 20%-1,15,000)</p><p>16 - 18 Pax = Raguler Rate 1,45,000 &nbsp;(Discount 20%-1,30,000)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Package Price for Bojra: (Weekday)</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 7,650 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 6,750 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 6,300 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 5,400 Per Person</p><p><strong>Package Price for Bojra: (Weekend)</strong></p><p>Couple Cabin - Attach Bath for 2 People BDT 8,500 Per Person</p><p>Couple Cabin - Common Bath for 2 People BDT 7,000 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Attach Bath for 3 People BDT 7,500 Per Person</p><p>Family Cabin - Common Bath for 3 People BDT 6,000 Per Person</p>', 'facility_images/xcR4xZdGKleuFEHM6lS0w8oTavJLZYb0QqEz10mq.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-06 04:49:23', '2025-04-06 04:49:23', '18'),
(433, 224, 12, NULL, '<p>Escape to the heart of Sunamganj for a classic Tanguar Haor experience. Live like a local aboard a traditional wooden boat for two days, exploring the wetlands\' majestic beauty and enchanting nearby attractions. This immersive tour is perfect for adventurers, taking you to hidden gems like the Jadukata River, watchtowers, and Shimul Bagan, all while soaking up the serenity of Tanguar Haor.<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Boat Packages Rate for Full Boat</strong></p><p><strong>Group Size</strong></p><p><br>28 - 32 Pax = Raguler Rate 2,60,000 (Discount 20%-2,08,000)</p><p>33 - 37 Pax = Raguler Rate 2,80,000 &nbsp;(Discount 20%-2,24,000)</p><p>38 - 40 Pax = Raguler Rate 3,00,000 &nbsp;(Discount 20%-2,40,000)<br><br>&nbsp;</p><p>১/<br>এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দাসহ- ৯৫০০ টাকা &nbsp;১ঃ২ জন</p><p>২/ এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দাসহ- ৮৫০০ টাকা ১ঃ৩ জন</p><p>৩/এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দাসহ- ৭৫০০ টাকা ১ঃ৪ জন</p><p>৪/ এটাচ বাথ ৮৫০০ টাকা ১ঃ২ জন</p><p>৫/ননএটাচ বাথ ৭৫৫০০ টাকা ১ঃ২ জন</p><p>৬ /ননএটাচ বাথ &nbsp;৬০০০ টাকা &nbsp;১ঃ৩ জন<br>&nbsp;<br>৭/ এটাচ বাথ ও বারান্দাসহ বাঙ্কার ব্যাড- ৬০০০ টাকা ১ঃ৮ জন<br><br><strong>(25% Discount Available on May Month.)</strong><br><br>NB : ২টি প্রাতরাশ । ২টি মধ্যাহ্ন ভোজ। ৪টি জলখাবার। ১টি নৈশ ভোজ চা ও সিজনাল ফল। ১ রাত বিলাসবহুল হাউসবোটি রাত্রিযাপন । সুনামগঞ্জ থেকে সুনামগঞ্জ ফুল ট্রিপ।<br>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/QrRfJ0qd4Nnk8iHVz1IoC4TadxWR41Z7hju13IjD.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-06 05:24:52', '2025-05-13 05:09:59', '18'),
(434, 263, 12, 'Summary', '<p>Sundarbans, a world-famous mangrove forest and a UNESCO heritage site, is one of the must-visit tourist attractions of Bangladesh. It lies within the vast delta formed in the confluence of countless rivers in the Bay of Bengal. Go Zayaan brings an amazing 3 days 2 nights tour which lets the travelers get up close and experience the real beauty of Sundarbans while having comfort and mouthwatering full-board meals for all the given days of the tour. Visit Harbaria Eco Tourism Point which offers an opportunity to see different exotic and local tree species like Sundori, Golpata, Gawa etc. Take a walk on the beautiful wooden bridge that leads deep into the forest and spot red crabs and different species of birds along with beautiful sceneries of Sundarbans. Explore the vast open land of Kotka sanctuary which offers the opportunity to see herds of deer and monkeys. For wildlife enthusiasts and bird watchers, Hiron point is famous for spotting Bengal tiger and other animals like Chitra Deer, Money, Wild Boar, Crocodile etc.The visit to Dublar Char will let travelers get a firsthand experience of the livelihood of the fishermen of The Sundarbans. Experience the eerie beauty of the forest at night while cruising through the forest. Experience the eerie beauty of the forest at night while cruising through the forest. The three days tour will have a different menu for each day to avoid monotony for the passengers on board. The cruise ship is a fully air-conditioned ship that is 148 feet long and 33 feet wide. There are 32 cabins of various accommodation types with attached washrooms.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Package Price for MV The Wave:</strong></p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> Single Cabin/ Couple Cabin/ Triple Share/ Family Cabin - Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 18,000 Per Person</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Remember, the cost per person is less if you have more people in your group.</p>', 'facility_images/lPbDBwQs6keaItJi7HN5oziZztFZYkPVnaRjnzZh.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-08 04:07:26', '2025-04-08 04:07:26', '17'),
