(458, 266, 12, NULL, '<p>Discover the magnificently mysterious beauty of the Sundarbans, which is home to the largest mangrove forest in the world. The tour lasts for three days and two nights, and it\'s meant to be a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity for guests. Armed guards ensure the safety of the journey from Khulna to the Sundarbans. Nobody else is allowed to bring firearms into the Sundarbans, nor are they permitted leave them there. Spend the night in the Sundarbans as you go to Kochikhali and Kotka. The area vegetation and fauna can be explored via boat at a dedicated facility. Full board meals on a delicious menu are included in the price of the cruise for the entire itinerary duration. The \"M.V Tanguare Haor\" is widely regarded as one of the most opulent and comfortable air-conditioned cruises available in the Sundarbans.</p><p><strong>Package Price for MV Tanguar Haor:</strong></p><p><strong>Cabin Type:</strong> Couple Cabin/ Twin Bed/ Triple Share/ Family Cabin- Attached Bath</p><p>Price: BDT 20,000 Per Person</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Remember, the cost per person is less if you have more people in your group.</p>', 'facility_images/7MRNBAQAFouVARVwx8YnXFHAne5bdsuF6lC0eCX6.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-08 06:08:23', '2025-04-08 06:08:23', '17'),
