(470, 267, 5, NULL, '<p>Sundarbans is the largest mangrove forest in the world and a natural world heritage listed by UNESCO. This mangrove forest hosts an amazing faunal &amp; floral diversity, including the probably largest remaining population of Royal Bengal tigers, the endangered estuarine crocodile, Ganges River dolphins as well as an astounding variety of birds. Join our luxurious cruise and explore this intricate maze of tidal waterways, a natural treasure of Bangladesh.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Food Menu</p><p>Day 1</p><p>Breakfast :&nbsp;Plain Porata, Vegetable, Mug Dal Bhuna, Fried Egg, Banana, Sundarbans Honey, Tea &amp; Coffee</p><p>Morning Snacks : Fruit Cake, Banana, Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Lunch: Plain Rice, Bhorta, Vegetable, Koral Fish Dopiaja, Chicken Potato Curry, Thick Daal, Mixed Salad, Shandhesh</p><p>Evening Snacks: Aloo Puri, Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Dinner : Plain Rice, Mixed Vegetable, Bhorta, Rui Fish Curry, Beef Aloo Curry, Daal Bhuna, Salad, Dessert- Papaya</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Day 2</p><p>Breakfast: Bhuna Khichuri, Begun Bhaji, Egg Malai Curry, Mixed Salad, Pickles, Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Morning Snacks : Orange/ Apple, Biscuit,Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Lunch:&nbsp;Plain rice, Shak Bhaji/Mixed Vegetable, Vatki/Rui fish Bhuna, Chicken Curry with Potato, Dal butter fry, Mixed Salad&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Evening Snacks: Vegetable, Pakora, Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Dinner:&nbsp;lain Porata, Fried Rice, BBQ Chicken ,BBQ Fish ,Solar Daal, Russian Salad ,Soft Drinks</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Day 3:&nbsp;</p><p>Breakfast: Ruti, Mixed Vegetable, Fried Egg, Sujir Halua, Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Morning Snacks: Dry Cake, Banana, Tea/ Coffee</p><p>Lunch: Plain Polau, Chinese Vegetable, Chicken Rezala, Egg Do Piaza, Ruhi Fish Fry, Mixed Salad, Chamcham</p><p>Evening Snacks : Chow mien, Tea/ Coffee</p>', 'facility_images/3VAcuinmci91EXZtZIMs1FeiubR9Pz6i2u7GSaUF.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-08 08:55:29', '2025-04-08 08:55:29', '17'),
