(561, 306, NULL, 'List of Documents Needed', '<p><strong>Documents Needed for Job Holders</strong></p><ol><li>At least Seven (07) Months Valid Passport with Old Passport (if you have one.)</li><li>Recent copy of 2 photographs taken in the last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 45 mm, Matt paper).</li><li>Copy of NID (Translated and Notarized)</li><li>Copy of latest income tax certificate.</li><li>Copy of Salary Certificate</li><li>Letter of Invitation (if any)</li><li>Inviter details (Example: relationship with applicant, contact details, passport copy, permanent resident card, bank statement, any utility bill)</li><li>Bank Statements for last six months with a bank solvency certificate (Minimum balance BDT 80,000 for each applicant).</li><li>Visiting Card.</li><li>No Objection Certificate (NOC) from employer or Government Order (GO)&nbsp;</li><li>Copy of office/organization ID Card.</li><li>Occupational verification document. (BMDC certificate for Doctor, BAR Council Certificate for Advocate)</li><li>Booking copy of Air Ticket and hotel reservation.</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Needed for Business Owners</strong></p><ol><li>At least Seven (07) Months Valid Passport with Old Passport (if you have one.)</li><li>Recent copy of 2 photographs taken in the last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 45 mm, Matt paper).</li><li>Copy of NID (Translated and Notarized)</li><li>Copy of latest trade license.</li><li>TIN Certificate</li><li>Letter of Invitation (if any)</li><li>Inviter details (Example: relationship with applicant, contact details, passport copy, permanent resident card, bank statement, any utility bill)</li><li>Bank Statements for last six months with a bank solvency certificate (Minimum balance BDT 80,000 for each applicant).</li><li>A blank copy of company letter head pad.</li><li>Visiting Card.</li><li>No Objection Certificate (NOC) from employer or Government Order (GO)&nbsp;</li><li>Copy of office/organization 