(562, 307, NULL, 'Summary', '<p>Visa Type: Tourist Visa (E-Visa)</p><p>Processing Time: 2 to 3 working days (Online Submission Only)</p><p>Note: <strong>Bookme</strong> will prepare and submit your visa application online within three working days. Please note that the total processing time for the application can take between 30 to 45 days.</p><p>GoZayaan Processing Fee: BDT 6,000 (Including embassy fee)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You can visit our Experience Center for a free Visa consultation with our travel experts and get started on your application.</p><p>Check out the address below:</p><p>IFCO Complex(2nd floor), GEC Circle, CDA Avenue, Chattogram.(Beside Hotel Jaman and restaurant).</p><p>For online support, please contact our 24/7 hotline number:</p><p>01967776777</p>', 'facility_images/IWhXvqPg3MTloFfFT5TZ11jGJWHfuTcg89CxAeif.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-27 08:29:06', '2025-04-27 08:29:06', NULL),
