(564, 307, NULL, 'List of Documents Needed', '<p><strong>Documents Needed for Job Holders</strong></p><ol><li>At least Seven (07) Months Valid Passport with Old Passport (if you have one.)</li><li>Previous e-visa copies (if any)</li><li>Recent copy of 2 photographs taken in the last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 50 mm, Matt paper).</li><li>Copy of NID (Translated and Notarized)</li><li>Bank Statements for last six months with a bank solvency certificate (Minimum balance BDT 500,000 for each applicant).</li><li>Income Tax Certificate of last 3 years.</li><li>Copy of Salary Certificate.</li><li>No Objection Certificate (NOC) from employer or Government Order (GO).</li><li>Copy of office/organization ID Card.</li><li>Visiting Card.</li><li>Marriage Certificate</li><li>Occupational verification document. (BMDC certificate for Doctor, BAR Council Certificate for Advocate)</li></ol><p><strong>Documents Needed for Business Owners</strong></p><ol><li>At least Seven (07) Months Valid Passport with Old Passport (if you have one.)</li><li>Previous e-visa copies (if any)</li><li>Recent copy of 2 photographs taken in the last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 50 mm, Matt paper).</li><li>Copy of NID (Translated and Notarized)</li><li>Bank Statements for last six months with a bank solvency certificate (Minimum balance BDT 500,000 for each applicant).</li><li>Copy of latest trade license.</li><li>TIN Certificate</li><li>Copies of the Certificate of Incorporation and Memorandum of Association for your company. Please include only the pages where the names of the directors are listed. (If you are an owner-director of a company)</li><li>Copy of letter head pad of the company.&nbsp;</li><li>Import export certificate (if any)</li><li>Marriage Certificate</li></ol><p><strong>Documents Needed for Students</strong></p><ol><li>At least Seven (07) Months Valid Passport with Old Passport (if you have one.)</li><li>Previous e-visa copies (if any)</li><li>Recent copy of 2 photographs taken in the last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 50 mm, Matt paper).</li><li>Copy of NID (Translated and Notarized)</li><li>Bank Statements for last six months with a bank solvency certificate (Minimum balance BDT 500,000 for each applicant).</li><li>Copy of ID Card of educational institute.</li><li>Parent / Guardian’s Bank Statement and supporting documents. (If personal account is not available)&nbsp;</li></ol><p><strong>Documents Needed for Other Relations</strong></p><ol><li>At least Seven (07) Months Valid Passport with Old Passport (if you have one.)</li><li>Previous e-visa copies (if any)</li><li>Copy of NID (Translated and Notarized)</li><li>Recent copy of 2 photographs taken in the last 3 months (white background only, photo size 35 mm X 45 mm, Matt paper).</li><li>Marriage Certificate Copy (For family application only)</li><li>Other financial documents (Fixed deposit/Sanchay Patra/Share documents)</li><li>Asset Valuation (Summary of Property, Bank Statement, Fixed Deposit, and Other Financial Documents)</li><li>Family information (Parents, Spouse, Child &amp; Sibling\'s name, date of birth &amp; current country of residence)</li></ol>', 'facility_images/ObebBNByifUTLfhsjnH179IyDiY13K6NcRaElWCw.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-04-27 08:29:38', '2025-04-27 08:29:38', NULL),
