on costs up to 30,000 Euros. The Insurance must fully cover the whole period of stay within the Schengen area.<br>*The conditions must be stated either on the insurance document or on a separate confirmation letter.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.09</strong></p><p><strong>Flight and hotel reservations</strong></p><p>Valid Flight and Hotel bookings or the inviter\'s residence address is required</p><p><strong>4.10</strong></p><p><strong>Invitation Letter (If Any)</strong></p><p>An original copy of Invitation letter from company/ Organization or Friends and Family with evidence.</p><p><strong>4.11</strong></p><p><strong>Forwarding Letter</strong></p><p>The applicant\'s name, designation, passport number, purpose, and duration of the visa.</p>', 'facility_images/IDHJ6HNg2abgY8btlG9Sncuv0fEo7WfPxE9z5S75.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-03 06:04:51', '2025-05-03 06:07:25', NULL),
