(623, 335, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Bhutan Tourist Visa (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>The applicant’s passport must be valid for at least six (6) months from the date of arrival and it must have at least one blank page for the immigration and border control officer to place the entry and exit stamps.</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>A recent passport size photograph is required.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Business Person</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>The applicant’s passport must be valid for at least six (6) months from the date of arrival and it must have at least one blank page for the immigration and border control officer to place the entry and exit stamps.</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>A recent passport size photograph is required.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Professionals(Doctor, Engineer, CA etc)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>The applicant’s passport must be valid for at least six (6) months from the date of arrival and it must have at least one blank page for the immigration and border control officer to place the entry and exit stamps.</p><p><strong>3.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>A recent passport size photograph is required.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Others</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>The applicant’s passport must be valid for at least six (6) months from the date of arrival and it must have at least one blank page for the immigration and border control officer to place the entry and exit stamps.</p><p><strong>4.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>A recent passport size photograph is required.</p>', 'facility_images/w3jyF9pfahOeu4KVWMQ8reItdA989aEkqilqY2fA.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-03 06:18:40', '2025-05-03 06:18:40', NULL),
