(625, 336, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Brazil Tourist Visa (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents. Also Applicant should, • be a genuine visitor • have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original passport bearing at least six (6) months validity. Moreover, the passport must have at least two blank pages.</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Online Visa Application Form</strong></p><p>Online application filled and signed according to the other documents by the applicant.</p><p><strong>1.03</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent Photographs, Passport size, with white background.</p><p><strong>1.04</strong></p><p><strong>NID and Birth Certificate</strong></p><p>NID Card Copy Or Birth Certificate copy is required.</p><p><strong>1.05</strong></p><p><strong>Financial Support</strong></p><p>Personal bank Statement for Last Six Months, Bank Solvency Certificate and Updated Income Tax Return Certificate.</p><p><strong>1.06</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Resident</strong></p><p>Recently Paid Utility bills; such as those for electricity, telephone, gas, or water, that are no older than six months. If the applicant resides in a flat, they may also give a copy of the building\'s main bill or a sub bill.</p><p><strong>1.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Occupation</strong></p><p>1.Salary certificate and Pay Slip. 2.Office ID card copy &amp; Visiting cards. 3. NOC</p><p><strong>1.08</strong></p><p><strong>Cover Letter and Tour Plan</strong></p><p>Applicants must mention the cost and reason for the visit in their cover letter. The travel itinerary and destinations must be listed in a tour plan.</p><p><strong>1.09</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of accommodation and Round Trip Air ticket booking</strong></p><p>Applicants must provide documentation of their hotel accommodations and round-trip airline reservations.</p><p><strong>1.10</strong></p><p><strong>Additional Documents</strong></p><p>Original and one photocopy of Police Clearance Certificate</p><p><strong>1.11</strong></p><p><strong>Important Note</strong></p><p>English Translation will be needed for Bangla documents and all documents have to be make Notary public.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Business Person</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original passport bearing at least six (6) months validity. Moreover, the passport must have at least two blank pages.</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Online Visa Application Form</strong></p><p>Online application filled and signed according to the other documents by the applicant.</p><p><strong>2.03</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent Photographs, Passport size, with white background.</p><p><strong>2.04</strong></p><p><strong>NID and Birth Certificate</strong></p><p>NID Card Copy Or Birth Certificate copy is required.</p><p><strong>2.05</strong></p><p><strong>Financial Support</strong></p><p>Personal bank Statement for Last Six Months, Bank Solvency Certificate and Updated Income Tax Return Certificate.</p><p><strong>2.06</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Resident</strong></p><p>Recently Paid Utility bills; such as those for electricity, telephone, gas, or water, that are no older than six months. If the applicant resides in a flat, they may also give a copy of the building\'s main bill or a sub bill.</p><p><strong>2.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Occupation</strong></p><p>1.Trade License updated. 2.Company memorandum (if business is limited) 3.Company pad &amp; Visiting cards.</p><p><strong>2.08</strong></p><p><strong>Cover Letter and Tour Plan</strong></p><p>Applicants must mention the cost and reason for the visit in their cover letter. The travel itinerary and destinations must be listed in a tour plan.</p><p><strong>2.09</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of accommodation and Round Trip Air ticket booking</strong></p><p>Applicants must provide documentation of their hotel accommodations and round-trip airline reservations.</p><p><strong>2.10</strong></p><p><strong>Additional Documents</strong></p><p>Original and one photocopy of Police Clearance Certificate</p><p><strong>2.11</strong></p><p><strong>Important Note</strong></p><p>English Translation will be needed for Bangla documents and all documents have to be make Notary public.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Professionals(Doctor, Engineer, CA etc)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original passport bearing at least six (6) months validity. Moreover, the passport must have at least two blank pages.</p><p><strong>3.02</strong></p><p><strong>Online Visa Application Form</strong></p><p>Online application filled and signed according to the other documents by the applicant.</p><p><strong>3.03</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent Photographs, Passport size, with white background.</p><p><strong>3.04</strong></p><p><strong>NID and Birth Certificate</strong></p><p>NID Card Copy Or Birth Certificate copy is required.</p><p><strong>3.05</strong></p><p><strong>Financial Support</strong></p><p>Personal bank Statement for Last Six Months, Bank Solvency Certificate and Updated Income Tax Return Certificate.</p><p><strong>3.06</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Resident</strong></p><p>Recently Paid Utility bills; such as those for electricity, telephone, gas, or water, that are no older than six months. If the applicant resides in a flat, they may also give a copy of the building\'s main bill or a sub bill.</p><p><strong>3.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Occupation</strong></p><p>1.Salary certificate and Pay Slip. 2.Office ID card copy &amp; Visiting cards. 3.BMDC certificate or letter from hospital if the applicant is a Doctor. 4.A Bar Council Certificate or letter from a law firm if the applicant is a lawyer.</p><p><strong>3.08</strong></p><p><strong>Cover Letter and Tour Plan</strong></p><p>Applicants must mention the cost and reason for the visit in their cover letter. The travel itinerary and destinations must be listed in a tour plan.</p><p><strong>3.09</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of accommodation and Round Trip Air ticket booking</strong></p><p>Applicants must provide documentation of their hotel accommodations and round-trip airline reservations.</p><p><strong>3.10</strong></p><p><strong>Additional Documents</strong></p><p>Original and one photocopy of Police Clearance Certificate</p><p><strong>3.11</strong></p><p><strong>Important Note</strong></p><p>English Translation will be needed for Bangla documents and all documents have to be make Notary public.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Others</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original passport bearing at least six (6) months validity. Moreover, the passport must have at least two blank pages.</p><p><strong>4.02</strong></p><p><strong>Online Visa Application Form</strong></p><p>Online application filled and signed according to the other documents by the applicant.</p><p><strong>4.03</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent Photographs, Passport size, with white background.</p><p><strong>4.04</strong></p><p><strong>NID and Birth Certificate</strong></p><p>NID Card Copy Or Birth Certificate copy is required.</p><p><strong>4.05</strong></p><p><strong>Financial Support</strong></p><p>Personal bank Statement for Last Six Months, Bank Solvency Certificate and Updated Income Tax Return Certificate.</p><p><strong>4.06</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Resident</strong></p><p>Recently Paid Utility bills; such as those for electricity, telephone, gas, or water, that are no older than six months. If the applicant resides in a flat, they may also give a copy of the building\'s main bill or a sub bill.</p><p><strong>4.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of Occupation</strong></p><p>1.A recommendation letter from the school / university or student card /evidence of school / university enrolment) if the applicant is a student.</p><p><strong>4.08</strong></p><p><strong>Cover Letter and Tour Plan</strong></p><p>Applicants must mention the cost and reason for the visit in their cover letter. The travel itinerary and destinations must be listed in a tour plan.</p><p><strong>4.09</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of accommodation and Round Trip Air ticket booking</strong></p><p>Applicants must provide documentation of their hotel accommodations and round-trip airline reservations.</p><p><strong>4.10</strong></p><p><strong>Additional Documents</strong></p><p>Original and one photocopy of Police Clearance Certificate</p><p><strong>4.11</strong></p><p><strong>Important Note</strong></p><p>English Translation will be needed for Bangla documents and all documents have to be make Notary public.</p>', 'facility_images/oOy0E07XAVbAMX3xHd4FKyhRkynEH9X2X1b0Gi0M.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-03 06:27:57', '2025-05-03 06:27:57', NULL),
