le period of stay within the Schengen area.<br>*The conditions must be stated either on the insurance document or on a separate confirmation letter.</p><p><strong>3.05</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification :</strong></p><p>Passport sized photograph (3.5cm by 4.5cm)<br>*The photo should be a recent whole face capture with a white background.<br>*Neutral face expression (No smile &amp; mouth closed) *Do not glue or staple the pictures to the application form.</p><p><strong>3.06</strong></p><p><strong>Flight and hotel reservations</strong></p><p>Valid Flight and Hotel bookings or the inviter\'s residence address is required</p><p><strong>3.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of civil status :</strong></p><p>*Marriage Certificate - if married (also NIkah Nama both in Bangla &amp; English,for Muslim Marriage in A4 size photocopy)<br>*Divorce Certificate - (talak nama) if applicable.<br>*Death certificate - if applicable.<br>*Birth certificate of children - if applicable.</p><p><strong>3.08</strong></p><p><strong>Invitation Letter (If Any)</strong></p><p>An original copy of the invitation letter from the company/ organization or Friends and Family with evidence.</p><p><strong>3.09</strong></p><p><strong>Applicant/Sponsor Financial Documents</strong></p><p>*Personal Bank Statement of the last 6 months &amp; Bank Solvency certificate.<br>*TIN certificate<br>*Income Tax certificate (Last 2 years), Tax Return (ITR)</p><p><strong>3.10</strong></p><p><strong>Applicant/Sponsor Proof of Occupation and Identity</strong></p><p>*Visiting Card<br>*If the applicant is a doctor, then he will show a BMDC certificate; If he is a lawyer, then he will have to show a Bar Council certificate; and others have to prove their occupation from their respective autonomous bodies.<br>*Valid Passport, NID, photo, and birth certificate.</p><p><strong>3.11</strong></p><p><strong>Forwarding Letter</strong></p><p>The applicant\'s name, designation, passport number, purpose, and duration of the visa.</p