(635, 340, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Czech Republic Tourist Visa (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>A valid passport that is original and at least six months validity is essential. Moreover, the passport must have at least two blank pages.<br>Note: Old passport is required (if any)</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>passport sized photographs (3.5x4.5cm)<br>Requirements:<br>a. Should not be older than 6 months.<br>b. A frontal view of the face covering 70-80% (32-26mm) of the biometric photo.<br>c. A uniform and white background.<br>d. Clear facial features<br>e. Head coverings are only accepted for religious reasons.<br>Do not glue or staple the pictures to the application form.</p><p><strong>1.03</strong></p><p><strong>Flight and hotel reservation</strong></p><p>Valid (existing) hotel booking / reservation with full address (name, street, city, zip code, contact information, booking ref.)<br> Flight reservation and travel itinerary</p><p><strong>1.04</strong></p><p><strong>Purpose of travel/stay</strong></p><p><br>Booking confirmation of an organised trip with detailed program, letter from applicant describing the planned trip.<br>Reservation of a return ticket or travel itinerary.</p><p><strong>1.05</strong></p><p><strong>Applicants / Sponsors Proof of Occupation and Identity</strong></p><p>*Office ID Card/Visiting Card<br>*Company Letter Pad: A letter from your employer on company letterhead, with contact details, stating that a leave of absence has been granted, the purpose and duration of the trip, and that you will be returning to your current job.<br>*Salary slips for the last 6 months<br>*Valid Passport, NID, Photo, and Birth certificate.</p><p><strong>1.06</strong></p><p><strong>Applicants / Sponsors Financial Documents</strong></p><p>*Personal Bank Statement of the last 6 months &amp; Bank Solvency certificate.<br>*TIN certificate<br>*Income Tax certificate (Last 2 years), Tax Return (ITR)</p><p><strong>1.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of civil status</strong></p><p>Marriage Certificate – if married (also Nikah Nama both in Bangla and English, for Muslim marriage in<br>A4 size Photocopy)<br> Divorce certificate (“talak namah”) – if applicable<br> Death Certificate – if applicable<br> Birth Certificate of your children –if applicable</p><p><strong>1.08</strong></p><p><strong>Travel Insurance</strong></p><p>Insurance must be valid for the whole Schengen area. The Insurance must cover the repatriation costs up to 30,000 Euros. The Insurance must fully cover the whole period of stay within the Schengen area.<br>*The conditions must be stated either on the insurance document or on a separate confirmation letter.</p><p><strong>1.09</strong></p><p><strong>Personal covering letter</strong></p><p>Explaining the purpose of your visit and who will bear the travel cost</p><p><strong>1.10</strong></p><p><strong>Additional Documents</strong></p><p>For minors below the age of 18 (if applicable) – proving legal parenthood:<br>a. copy of either birth certificate / proof of adoption / custody decree in case parents are divorced or<br>- if applicable - death certificate of parent ( Swedish or English translation is required)<br>“Letter of consent” from legal guardian, including his / her passport copy – legalized by a notary public<br>(only required in cases the legal guardian is not present during the visa appointment)</p><p><strong>1.11</strong></p><p><strong>Invitation Letter (If Any)</strong></p><p>An original copy of Invitation letter from company/ Organization or Friends and Family with evidence.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Business Person</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>A valid passport that is original and at least six months validity is essential. Moreover, the passport must have at least two blank pages.<br>Note: Old passport is required (if any)</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>passport sized photographs (3.5x4.5cm)<br>Requirements:<br>a. Should not be older than 6 months.<br>b. A frontal view of the face covering 70-80% (32-26mm) of the biometric photo.<br>c. A uniform and white background.<br>d. Clear facial features<br>e. Head coverings are only accepted for religious reasons.<br>Do not glue or staple the pictures to the application form.</p><p><strong>2.03</strong></p><p><strong>Flight and hotel reservation</strong></p><p>Valid (existing) hotel booking / reservation with full address (name, street, city, zip code, contact information, booking ref.)<br> Flight reservation and travel itinerary</p><p><strong>2.04</strong></p><p><strong>Purpose of travel/stay</strong></p><p><br>Booking confirmation of an organised trip with detailed program, letter from applicant describing the planned trip.<br>Reservation of a return ticket or travel itinerary.</p><p><strong>2.05</strong></p><p><strong>Applicants / Sponsors Proof of Occupation and Identity</strong></p><p>*Company memorandum.<br>*Visiting card.<br>*Updated Trade License<br>*Valid Passport copy, NID, Photo, Birth certificate.</p><p><strong>2.06</strong></p><p><strong>Applicants / Sponsors Financial Documents</strong></p><p>*Personal Bank Statement of last 6 months &amp; Bank Solvency certificate.<br>*Company Bank Statement of last 6 months &amp; Bank Solvency certificate (if business holder)<br>*TIN certificate<br>*Income Tax certificate (Last 2 years), Tax Return (ITR)<br>*Income Tax Certificate of the Company (Last 2 Yea