r on a separate confirmation letter.</p><p><strong>4.08</strong></p><p><strong>Flight and hotel reservation</strong></p><p>Valid round trip Air Ticket confirmation and Hotel confirmation for the whole duration of the stay, or other documents proving accommodation is required.</p><p><strong>4.09</strong></p><p><strong>Cover Letter and Tour Plan</strong></p><p>A personal letter from the applicant covering personal details, the purpose of the visit, and outlining who will be responsible for the full costs of the trip. The accommodation details also need to include.<br>Also in a tour plan applicants have to mention the travel Itinerary and places.<br>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.10</strong></p><p><strong>Forwarding Letter</strong></p><p>The applicant\'s name, designation, passport number, purpose, and duration of the visa.</p><p><strong>4.11</strong></p><p><strong>Invitation Letter (If Any)</strong></p><p>An original copy of Invitation letter from company/ Organization or Friends and Family with evidence.</p>', 'facility_images/iBEI7WmrFHRY7Osoi2EBk394V8tdk6p34jSF9h1i.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:10:14', '2025-05-04 08:10:14', NULL),
