(661, 354, NULL, 'Pre-Approved On Arrival Visa', '<p>The applicant must submit the necessary authentic and valid documents for a Mauritius Pre-Approved On Arrival Visa through online. Once approved by the Embassy of Mauritius, an electronic copy (softcopy) of the Visa will be sent to the Applicant for collection.</p>', 'facility_images/9QHL8CXSMukYX0rj3RBZ3oQIBDB4dnmKJXte1ncW.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:16:19', '2025-05-04 08:16:19', NULL),
(662, 354, NULL, 'Tourist Visa', '<p>The Standard “ Pre-Approved On Arrival Visa for Tourist” is valid for 30 days (from VISA issue date) for a single journey to Mauritius for the purpose of Tour / Holidaying / Vacation. The Visitor is allowed to stay in Mauritius for no more than 30 consecutive days. Visitors under tourist visas are not allowed to accept any unauthorized employment, attend school, or represent the foreign information media during their stay in Mauritius.</p>', 'facility_images/ZWnrY2hcuTX3DYyysOC7VpkntUwwMPMm3B3kZITy.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:16:40', '2025-05-04 08:16:40', NULL),
(663, 354, NULL, 'Processing Time', '<p>Total approximate processing time is 5 to 7 working days (Time may vary depending on applicant’s profile and embassy actually processing time).</p>', 'facility_images/U5o1cvIXVuXhmr1u57RrA1zHjATqVcYO7GJ7UitS.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:16:57', '2025-05-04 08:16:57', NULL),
(664, 355, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Nepal Tourist Visa (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent passport size photographs with white background and without border.</p><p><strong>1.03</strong></p><p><strong>NID</strong></p><p>A Copy of National ID Card both page</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Business Person</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent passport size photographs with white background and without border.</p><p><strong>2.03</strong></p><p><strong>NID</strong></p><p>A Copy of National ID Card both page</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Professionals(Doctor, Engineer, CA etc)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>3.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent passport size photographs with white background and without border.</p><p><strong>3.03</strong></p><p><strong>NID</strong></p><p>A Copy of National ID Card both page</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Others</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>4.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification</strong></p><p>Two recent passport size photographs with white background and without border.</p><p><strong>4.03</strong></p><p><strong>NID</strong></p><p>A Copy of National ID Card both page</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/ja4sMvwhfhOJBYkV2PJbuD0AnhvSjMrA2Fr5UtC6.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:26:18', '2025-05-04 08:26:18', NULL),
(665, 355, NULL, 'Important Notes', '<p>Please contact the Visa department for Document processing after the payment. Visa rate may change without any prior notice</p>', 'facility_images/RSDd9JHZf0nKLJoIqXtSxx3op5BgX9nOq1GAOeWT.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:26:51', '2025-05-04 08:26:51', NULL),
(666, 356, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Pakistan eVISA (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Machine Scanned copy of Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Soft copy of recent passport size photo (35mm x 50mm) with white background. Photo must be lab copy(raw file), Please, DO NOT use Scanned photographs.</p><p><strong>1.03</strong></p><p><strong>Travel History</strong></p><p>If the applicant has traveled to Pakistan or any other country during the last 5 years, he/she must mention the following:<br>1. Country name<br>2. Visa number<br>3. Entry &amp; exit date from the country<br>4. A clearly scanned copy of the visa</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Business Person</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Machine Scanned copy of Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Soft copy of recent passport size photo (35mm x 50mm) with white background. Photo must be lab copy(raw file), Please, DO NOT use Scanned photographs.</p><p><strong>2.03</strong></p><p><strong>Travel History</strong></p><p>If the applicant has traveled to Pakistan or any other country during the last 5 years, he/she must mention the following:<br>1. Country name<br>2. Visa number<br>3. Entry &amp; exit date from the country<br>4. A clearly scanned copy of the visa</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Professionals(Doctor, Engineer, CA etc)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Machine Scanned copy of Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>3.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Soft copy of recent passport size photo (35mm x 50mm) with white background. Photo must be lab copy(raw file), Please, DO NOT use Scanned photographs.</p><p><strong>3.03</strong></p><p><strong>Travel History</strong></p><p>If the applicant has traveled to Pakistan or any other country during the last 5 years, he/she must mention the following:<br>1. Country name<br>2. Visa number<br>3. Entry &amp; exit date from the country<br>4. A clearly scanned copy of the visa</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Others</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Machine Scanned copy of Original Passport with validity of minimum six months after the intended date of departure and minimum two blank pages for visa stamp.</p><p><strong>4.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Soft copy of recent passport size photo (35mm x 50mm) with white background. Photo must be lab copy(raw file), Please, DO NOT use Scanned photographs.</p><p><strong>4.03</strong></p><p><strong>Travel History</strong></p><p>If the applicant has traveled to Pakistan or any other country during the last 5 years, he/she must mention the following:<br>1. Country name<br>2. Visa number<br>3. Entry &amp; exit date from the country<br>4. A clearly scanned copy of the visa</p>', 'facility_images/Wv6uWfsyr9hwKAo1KPBhn2Ym5POs2AyqMH1p5S6j.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-04 08:46:02', '2025-05-04 08:46:02', NULL),
