(672, 360, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Qatar Tourist Visa (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Passport Scan copy (with a six-months validity) Required</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Face must take up 70% to 80% of the photo. The size of the photo should not be more than 2 MB. Only JPEG or JPG images must be used, photo must be in color and size must be in 35 mm * 45 mm.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Business Person</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Passport Scan copy (with a six-months validity) Required</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Face must take up 70% to 80% of the photo. The size of the photo should not be more than 2 MB. Only JPEG or JPG images must be used, photo must be in color and size must be in 35 mm * 45 mm.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Professionals(Doctor, Engineer, CA etc)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Passport Scan copy (with a six-months validity) Required</p><p><strong>3.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Face must take up 70% to 80% of the photo. The size of the photo should not be more than 2 MB. Only JPEG or JPG images must be used, photo must be in color and size must be in 35 mm * 45 mm.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Others</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Passport Scan copy (with a six-months validity) Required</p><p><strong>4.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>Face must take up 70% to 80% of the photo. The size of the photo should not be more than 2 MB. Only JPEG or JPG images must be used, photo must be in color and size must be in 35 mm * 45 mm.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/mZooYu4m8v9VulwFJURW9xU5KjdgeNgsKbChNdnx.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-05 05:23:18', '2025-05-05 05:23:18', NULL),
(673, 360, NULL, 'Important Notes', '<p><strong>e-Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The applicant who require a visa to enter Qatar as a \'Tourist\'. Once approved by the Embassy of Qatar, an electronic copy (softcopy) of the Visa will be sent to the registered email account.<br>Disclaimer: The applicant must have a running USA/Schengen/Australia/Canada/New Zealand/Uk Visa to become eligible for applying Qatar Tourist Visa</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Tourist Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Qatar tourist Visa is for anyone who wishes to travel to Qatar for tourism or visit friends and family. The stay permit is 30 days. Visitors under tourist visas are not allowed to accept any unauthorized employment, attend school, or represent the foreign information media during their stay in Qatar.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br><i><strong>Please contact the Visa department for Document processing after the payment. Visa rate may change without any prior notice</strong></i></p>', 'facility_images/dVMEYlN0kXNsUcGOrnVfUQbmqA9JXXV5FkDV6eR8.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-05 05:24:09', '2025-05-05 05:24:09', NULL),
