 or on a separate confirmation letter.</p><p><strong>4.05</strong></p><p><strong>Photo Specification :</strong></p><p>Passport sized photograph (3.5cm by 4.5cm)<br>*The photo should be a recent whole face capture with a white background.<br>*Neutral face expression (No smile &amp; mouth closed) *Do not glue or staple the pictures to the application form.</p><p><strong>4.06</strong></p><p><strong>Flight and hotel reservations</strong></p><p>Valid Flight and Hotel bookings or the inviter\'s residence address is required</p><p><strong>4.07</strong></p><p><strong>Proof of civil status :</strong></p><p>*Marriage Certificate - if married (also NIkah Nama both in Bangla &amp; English,for Muslim Marriage in A4 size photocopy)<br>*Divorce Certificate - (talak nama) if applicable.<br>*Death certificate - if applicable.<br>*Birth certificate of children - if applicable.</p><p><strong>4.08</strong></p><p><strong>Invitation Letter (If Any)</strong></p><p>An original copy of the invitation letter from the company/ organization or Friends and Family with evidence.</p><p><strong>4.09</strong></p><p><strong>Applicant/Sponsor Financial Documents</strong></p><p>*Personal Bank Statement of the last 6 months &amp; Bank Solvency certificate.<br>*TIN certificate<br>*Income Tax certificate (Last 2 years), Tax Return (ITR)</p><p><strong>4.10</strong></p><p><strong>Applicant/Sponsor Proof of Occupation and Identity</strong></p><p>*Valid Passport, NID, photo, and birth certificate.<br>*Visa request letter from the educational institute or student card/evidence of school enrollment (if student)</p><p><strong>4.11</strong></p><p><strong>Forwarding Letter</strong></p><p>The applicant\'s name, designation, passport number, purpose, and duration of the visa.</p><p><strong>4.12</strong></p><p><strong>Additional Documents :</strong></p><p>For minors below the age of 18,proof of legal parenthood (if applicable) :<br>*copy of either birth certificate or proof of adoption (if adopted).<br>*custody decree in case parents are divorced or death certificate of parents (if applicable).<br>*\'Letter of Consent\' from the legal guardian including his/her passport copy legalized by a notary public. (only required in case the legal guardian is not present during the Visa appointment.).</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/Z7Knseqo0uSU6u5iV0DGwu0mCUtnzto6nnwtN6WL.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-05 06:18:39', '2025-05-05 06:18:39', NULL),
