(691, 370, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Tanzania eVISA (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>e-Visa</strong></p><p>The applicant must submit the necessary authentic and valid documents for a Tanzania eVisa through online. Once approved by the Embassy of Tanzania, an electronic copy (softcopy) of the Visa will be sent to the Applicant for collection.</p><p><strong>Tourist Visa</strong></p><p>The Standard “eVISA for Tourist” is valid for 90 days (from eVISA issue date) for a single journey to Tanzania for the purpose of Tour / Holidaying / Vacation. The Visitor is allowed to stay in Tanzania for no more than 90 consecutive days. Visitors under tourist visas are not allowed to accept any unauthorized employment, attend school, or represent the foreign information media during their stay in Tanzania.</p>', 'facility_images/1uO401SN6H5yGLIod99U26H78GvkvcvMvAgJpJE2.png', 1, NULL, '2025-05-06 06:07:06', '2025-05-06 06:07:06', NULL),
