(694, 372, NULL, 'Important Notes', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>e-Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Applicant must submit for \'UAE Electronic Visa\' (eVISA) Online with Valid / Authentic documents. Once approved by the Immigration Department of UAE, an Electronic Copy (Softcopy) of the Visa will be sent to the Applicant’s Email.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Tourist Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The \'UAE Tourist Visa\' is valid for 30 days / 60 days (from entry date) for a Single or Multiple Journey to UAE for the purpose of Tour / Holidaying / Vacation. The Visitor is allowed to stay in UAE for no more than 30 or 60 consecutive days. Visitors under Tourist Visa are not allowed to accept any unauthorized employment, or attend school, or represent the foreign information media during their stay in UAE.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>UNITED ARAB EMIRATES is not issuing E-visa for Bangladeshi passport holders at this moment</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br><strong>&nbsp;Please contact the Visa department for Document processing after the payment. Visa rate may change without any prior notice</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/Ao2f1g50sayqph6lQTJIJrGmLd6jMAIaT679YKee.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-06 06:20:06', '2025-05-06 06:22:27', NULL),
(695, 373, NULL, 'Required Documents for Visa', '<p><strong>Eligibility to Apply for Visa</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Any Bangladeshi Nationals are Eligible to Apply for Uzbekistan eVISA (having a valid MRP / E-Passport with at least 6 months validity) subject to provide some required Documents.<br>Also Applicant should,<br>• be a genuine visitor<br>• have enough funds to support his/her stay and leave</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Documents Requirements</strong></p><h2><strong>1. Service Holder</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Soft Copy of a Passport Information Page with Minimum 6 month’s validity required</p><p><strong>1.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>One Copy Recent Passport Size Lab Print Photo (Soft Copy)<br>The photo must have a size of 35x45 mm with a resolution of 300 dpi. Image dimensions should not exceed 1 Mb. The photo must meet the standards ICAO</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2 Business Person.</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Soft Copy of a Passport Information Page with Minimum 6 month’s validity required</p><p><strong>2.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>One Copy Recent Passport Size Lab Print Photo (Soft Copy)<br>The photo must have a size of 35x45 mm with a resolution of 300 dpi. Image dimensions should not exceed 1 Mb. The photo must meet the standards ICAO</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Professionals(Doctor, Engineer, CA etc)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3.01</strong></p><p><strong>Passport</strong></p><p>Soft Copy of a Passport Information Page with Minimum 6 month’s validity required</p><p><strong>3.02</strong></p><p><strong>Photo</strong></p><p>One Copy Recent Passport Size Lab Print Photo (Soft Copy)<br>The photo must have a size of 35x45 mm with a resolution of 300 dpi. Image dimensions should not exceed 1 Mb. The photo must meet the standards ICAO</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Others</strong></h2><