(696, 373, NULL, 'Important Notes', '<p>Please contact the Visa department for Document processing after the payment. Visa rate may change without any prior notice</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>e-Visa</p><p>The applicant must submit the necessary authentic and valid documents for Uzbekistan eVisa through online. Once approved by the Embassy of Uzbekistan, an electronic copy (softcopy) of the Visa will be sent to the applicants email / applicant can download it from the visa application portal.</p><p>Tourist Visa</p><p>The Standard “eVISA for Tourist” is valid for 90 days (from eVISA issue date) for a single journey to Uzbekistan for the purpose of Tour / Holidaying / Vacation. The Visitor is allowed to stay in Uzbekistan for no more than 30 consecutive days. Visitors under tourist visas are not allowed to accept any unauthorized employment, attend school, or represent the foreign information media during their stay in Uzbekistan.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Uzbekistan is not issuing E-visa for Bangladeshi passport holders at this moment</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/sOX5z1ZertIBJ8hysVyg68f5WMIKthhThzlZrPFI.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-06 06:30:10', '2025-05-06 06:30:10', NULL),
(697, 281, 12, NULL, '<p>Discover the timeless charm of Tanguar Haor with a classic two-day adventure. Begin your journey as you step aboard a beautifully crafted wooden boat, guided by experienced local boatmen. Cruise through the serene waters mirroring the vast sky above, immersing yourself in a voyage steeped in tradition that showcases the harmonious relationship between the land and its inhabitants. As you drift through the untouched wetlands, you\'ll be captivated by the dance of light and water, surrounded by lush landscapes and captivating nearby attractions that exude an untarnished sense of wonder. This traditional excursion not only allows you to deeply connect with nature but also offers a glimpse into the rich cultural fabric of the region, making it the perfect escape for those in search of an authentic exploration of Tanguar Haor\'s enchanting beauty.</p><p><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t6c/1/16/1f1e7_1f1e9.png\" alt=\"🇧🇩\"> ভ্রমণস্থান গুলো যেগুলো আমরা ঘুরে দেখাবো:</p><p>১ম দিন:</p><p>১. টাঙ্গুয়ার হাওর</p><p>২. ওয়াচ টাওয়ার</p><p>৩. লাকমাছড়া</p><p>৪. নীলাদ্রি লেক</p><p>৭. টেকেরঘাট</p><p>৫. শিমুল বাগান</p><p>৬. বারিক্কা টিলা<br><br>প্রাইসঃ<br><br>১/বাঙ্কার ক্যাবিন ( নন- এটাচড বাথরুম) - ৪জন ৪৫০০/- (জনপ্রতি)।<br>&nbsp;</p><p>২/কাঁপল ক্যাবিন ( নন- এটাচড বাথরুম) - ২ জন ৫৫০০/-(জন প্রতি)।<br>&nbsp;</p><p>৩/বড় লকডোর ক্যাবিন্ এটাচড বাথরুম। ৩জন ৬৫০০/- (জনপ্রতি)।<br>&nbsp;</p><p>৪/কাপল লকডোর ক্যাবিন (এটাচড বাথরুম) ২ জন ৮৫০০/-(জনপ্রতি)।<br>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'facility_images/uGDoIyB66cjFAFjz65LHJPgq6YHWNfXX9g98H3oJ.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-05-10 11:24:25', '2025-05-29 05:59:49', '16'),
