(726, 285, 6, NULL, '<h2><strong>Additional information</strong></h2><p>Information about the Boat: ITA Express</p><p>Total Rooms: 8</p><p>Attached Rooms: 4 couple rooms (2 people each, total 8 people)</p><p>Non-Attached Rooms: 2 couple rooms (2 people each, total 4 people)</p><p>Non-Attached Family Rooms: 2 rooms (6 people each, total 12 people)</p><p>Common Washrooms: 1 high commode, 1 low commode</p><p>Spacious Rooftop Garden: For natural ventilation</p><p>Spacious Lobby: For social gatherings</p><p>Modern Sound System</p><p>Indoor Sports Items</p><p>Double Cylinder Engine</p><p>Sufficient Life Jackets and Buoys</p><p>Modern Fire Extinguisher Cylinder</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Things to keep in mind</p><ul><li>An adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.</li><li>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.</li><li>The times mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather conditions, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers, and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstances.</li><li>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.</li><li>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.</li><li>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.</li><li>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitants. Travelers are asked to seek help from the tour operator/host/organizer in case they need to contact any local people.</li><li>There is no separate dining space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.</li><li>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.</li><li>In the case of a group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to Lakmachora on a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-05-14 06:50:38', '2025-05-14 06:50:38', '21'),
