(814, 384, 5, NULL, '<h2><strong>Description</strong></h2><p>Located in north-eastern Bangladesh, Tanguar haor is a river basin and a unique wetland ecosystem of national importance. The tour is ideal for you if you want to experience both adventures and serenity. You’ll have a traditional wooden boat with the necessary amenities as your home during the tour. During the tour, you’ll have mouth-watering delicacies more than three times a day while watching the beauty of the wetland from your private boat. The tour will also let you explore the picturesque beauty of Shimul Bagan, bathe in the mirror-like clear water, visit the popular lakes, and enjoy the view of the hills around. Hence, the tour will give you both tranquility to your soul and stories to tell.<br><br>🍽️ খাবার মেনু<br>প্রথম দিন:<br>সকালের নাস্তা: ভুনা খিচুড়ি, ডিম কারী,সালাদ, আচার, চা, পানি।&nbsp;<br>স্ন্যাকস: বিস্কুট/চা,ফ্রুটস (১১:৩০)<br>দুপুরের খাবার: ভাত,ভর্তা+সবজি, হাওরের মাছের তরকারি, &nbsp;দেশি মুরগি ভুনা,ডাল,মিনারেল পানি,সালাদ।<br>সান্ধ্যকালীন স্ন্যাকস:নুডলস/মুড়িমাখা চা ও পানি।<br>রাতের খাবার:ভাত,আলু ভর্তা/সবজি,হাওরের মাছ ভাজা/ভুনা,দেশী হাঁসের ভুনা,ডাল,পানি,সফট ড্রিংকস,সালাদ।<br>দ্বিতীয় দিন:<br>সকালের নাস্তা:&nbsp;<br>ভুনা খিচুড়ি, ডিম, সালাদ, আচার, চা,পানি।&nbsp;<br>স্ন্যাকস: বিস্কুট/ফ্রুটস,চা ও পানি&nbsp;<br>দুপুরের খাবার: ভাত, ভর্তা/সবজি,হাওরের মাছ,মুরগী ভুনা, ডাল,পানি,সালাদ।<br>সান্ধ্যকালীন স্ন্যাকস:নুডলস/মুড়িমাখা চা ও পানি।<br><strong>শিশু পলিসি&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>০-৩ বছর ঃ ফ্রি&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>বাবা মায়ের সাথে থাকবে।</strong><br><strong>আলাদা কোনো সুবিধা/খাবার/ বিছানা পাবে না।&nbsp;</strong><br><strong>০৪-০৭বছর -৩৫০০/-</strong><br><strong>বাবা মায়ের সাথে থাকবে।আলাদা খাবার পাবে।</strong><br><strong>৮ &nbsp;বছরের ওপরে ।</strong><br><strong>বড়দের সমান খরচ।</strong><br><strong>সকল সুবিধা সমান ভাবেই নিতে হবে।</strong><br>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-05-17 08:55:58', '2025-05-28 09:42:59', '20'),
(815, 384, NULL, NULL, '<h2><strong>স্বপ্নডিঙ্গি - A Premium Water Villa</strong></h2><p>Things to keep in mind</p><p>An adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.<br>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.<br>The times mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather conditions, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers, and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstances.<br>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.<br>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.<br>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.<br>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitants. Travelers are asked to seek help from the tour operator/host/organizer in case they need to contact any local people.<br>There is no separate dining space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.<br>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.<br>In the case of a group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.<br>If anyone wants to travel to Lakmachora on a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</p>', NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-05-17 08:57:33', '2025-06-01 05:39:10', '16'),
