(906, 394, 5, NULL, '<h2><strong>Description</strong></h2><p>Nestled in north-eastern Bangladesh, Tanguar Haor is a remarkable river basin and wetland ecosystem of national significance. This tour is perfect for those seeking a blend of adventure and peace. You\'ll stay on a traditional wooden boat, equipped with all necessary amenities, serving as your home throughout the journey. Savor delectable meals more than three times a day as you take in the stunning views of the wetland from your floating abode. The tour includes exploring the scenic Shimul Bagan, swimming in crystal-clear waters, visiting popular lakes, and enjoying the surrounding hills. To elevate your experience, live local musical sessions are arranged, providing soulful tranquility and memorable tales to share.</p><p>Places that will be covered in this tour are</p><ul><li>Tanguar Haor</li><li>Watch Tower</li><li>Jadukata River</li><li>Barikka Tila</li><li>Teker Ghat</li><li>Shahid Siraj Lake / Quarry Lake / Niladri Lake</li><li>Khorchar Haor</li><li>Shonir Haor</li></ul><p><strong>Food Menu:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>Day - 1&nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Welcome Drinks&nbsp;</li><li><strong>Breakfast:</strong>&nbsp;Khichuri, Fried Egg, Fried Chicken, Fried Eggplant, Pickles, Salad,Drinking Water, Tea</li><li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Spicy Puffed Rice, Fruits, Tea, Drinking Water.</li><li><strong>Lunch</strong>: Rice, Boal Fish, Fish Bhorta, Small Fish Fry, Mashed Potato, Murighanta, Salad, Drinking Water, Tea, Sweets.</li><li><strong>Aftenoon Snacks:</strong> Eggplant, Chop, Tea.</li><li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Rice, Mashed Brinjal, Small Fish/Medium Fish Fry, Roasted Duck, Daal, Salad, Drinking Water, Tea</li></ul><p><strong>Day - 2</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Breakfast: </strong>Chicken Akhni, Small Fish Fry, Pickles, Salad, Drinking Water, Tea,</li><li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Cookies/ Singara/ Noodles, Tea</li><li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Rice, Kalbaus/ Aair Fish, Roasted Chicken,Mashed Tomato, Daal, Salad,Drinking Water, Tea.</li><li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Eggplant Chop, Coffee.</li></ul>', NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-05-22 05:10:14', '2025-05-22 05:10:14', '9'),
(907, 394, 6, NULL, '<h2><strong>হিমাদ্রি -A Luxury house boat</strong></h2><p>Things to keep in mind</p><p>An adequate amount of tea will be served on the boat. Travelers can have tea anytime they want.<br>There is a water filter on the boat. Travelers can drink water from that water filter.<br>The times mentioned in the itinerary are subject to change due to weather conditions, tides in the river, convenience of the travelers, and other unavoidable circumstances. Travelers are requested to cooperate with the operator/host/organizer in case of such circumstances.<br>The travelers are requested to contact with the tour operator/host/organizer incase they face any kind of trouble/problem during the tour.<br>Always be respectful of the rules and guidelines of the tourist spots.<br>Do not litter, use a disposable bag as a portable trash bin.<br>Travelers are strongly encouraged not to misbehave with any local inhabitants. Travelers are asked to seek help from the tour operator/host/organizer in case they need to contact any local people.<br>There is no separate dining space on this boat. Everyone will have their meals on the open deck of the boat.<br>Consumption of any sort of drugs is strictly prohibited.<br>In the case of a group tour, there will be other people who will travel with you.<br>If anyone wants to travel to Lakmachora on a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</p>', NULL, 1, NULL, '2025-05-22 05:10:34', '2025-06-01 05:44:22', '11'),
