here will be other people who will travel with you.</li><li>If anyone wants to travel to Lakmachora on a bike then the traveler will have to bear the bike fare.</li></ul>', 'facility_images/4oedzVSa1wcKEP25mXSJlHW32cO5cGvnoYxgSaLm.jpg', 1, NULL, '2025-07-03 08:30:35', '2025-07-03 08:30:35', '20'),
